0not%20today's%20Chief%20Ministers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20worker%20from%20Banaras%20have%20ever%20seen%20Modi-ji%2C%20let%20alone%C2%A0%20stopping%20him%20on%20the%20road%20and%20talking%20to%20him...%20This%20is%20the%20BJP%20of%202G.%20It%20is%20not%20run%20by%20politicians%20but%20by%20corporates%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rai%2C%20who%20was%20named%20by%20the%20Congress%20as%20its%20candidate%20this%20weekend%2C%20will%20be%20contesting%20against%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20for%20the%20third%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20lost%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20both%20in%202014%20and%202019%20--%20indicating%20that%20Varanasi%2C%20a%20BJP%20stronghold%2C%20does%20not%20place%20much%20premium%20on%20the%20%26quot%3Bson%20of%20the%20soil%26quot%3B%20argument.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20PM%20Modi%20won%20with%20over%2056%25%20vote%20share%2C%20while%20Mr%20Rai%20managed%20to%20get%20around%2075%2C000%20votes.%20In%202019%2C%20Mr%20Rai%20got%20around%2014%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20votes%20compared%20to%20PM%20Modi's%2063%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20different%20note%2C%20Mr%20Rai%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20state%20Congress%20chief%2C%20assured%20that%20the%20candidates%20for%20the%20Congress%20bastion%20Raebareli%20and%20Amethi%2C%20which%20has%20gone%20over%20to%20the%20BJP%20in%202019%2C%20will%20be%20announced%20shortly.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20as%20the%20suspense%20about%20Varanasi%20was%20removed%2C%20that%20of%20Amethi%20and%20Raebareli%20will%20also%20be%20removed.%20The%20people%20from%20both%20constituencies%20desire%20that%20someone%20from%20the%20Gandhi%20family%20contest%20elections%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711292460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fg239tvh8_ajai-rai_625x300_24_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcount-how-many-ti