%2Fphoto%2F108753280.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EOn%20his%2045th%20birthday%2C%20Emraan%20Hashmi%20graced%20Baba%20Siddiqui's%20annual%20iftar%20party.%20Hosts%20Baba%20and%20Zeeshan%20Siddiqui%20arranged%20a%20modest%20cake-cutting%20ceremony%20for%20him.%20Emraan%2C%20in%20a%20printed%20blue%20kurta%20and%20white%20pyjamas%2C%20charmed%20attendees%20as%20he%20fed%20them%20slices%20of%20a%20large%20chocolate%20cake%20amidst%20paparazzi.%20Numerous%20Bollywood%20and%20TV%20personalities%20also%20attended%20the%20event.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Femraan-hashmi-cuts-cake-as-he-celebrates-his-birthday-at-baba-siddiqui-and-zeeshan-siddiquis-annual-iftar-party-see-photos%2Farticleshow%2F108753280.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kerala%20Moves%20SC%20Against%20President%20Murmu%20for%20Withholding%20Assent%20to%20State%20Bills%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20On%20March%2023%2C%20Kerala%20moved%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20against%20President%20Draupadi%20Murmu%20for%20withholding%20assent%20to%20four%20out%20of%20seven%20bills%20passed%20by%20the%20state%20assembly%2C%20as%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barandbench.com%2Fnews%2Fkerala-moves-supreme-court-against-president-withholding-assent-four-bills%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBarAndBench%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKerala%20has%20also%20moved%20the%20court%20against%20Governor%20Mohammed%20Arif%20Khan%20for%20keeping%20his%20assent%20on%20bills%20pending%20for%20months%20%E2%80%93%20from%20between%20seven%20to%2024%20months%20%E2%80%94%20and%20referring%20them%20to%20Murmu%20when%20there%20was%20no%20need%20to.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EFour%20of%20seven%20bills%20not%20given%20assent%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELast%20year%2C%20the%20Kerala%20state%20assembly%20passed%20several%20bills%20including%20seven%20%E2%80%94%20some%20of%20which%20were%20also%20in%20public%20interest%20%E2%80%94%20the%20state%20said%20as%20it%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20against%20Murmu%20for%20withholding%20assent%20to%20four%20of%20those%20seven%20bills.%20The%20president%20has%20also%20not%20given%20any%20reason%20for%20withholding%20assent%20to%20these%20bills%2C%20Kerala%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Kerala%20government%20has%20argued%20that%20the%20president%20withholding%20assent%20to%20the%20bills%20%E2%80%9Csubverts%20and%20disrupts%E2%80%9D%20the%20federal%20structure%20of%20the%20Indian%20constitution%2C%20reported%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBarAndBench%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20seven%20bills%20included%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20amendments%20to%20the%20University%20Laws%20(dated%202021%20and%202022)%2C%20the%20Kerala%20Lokayukta%20Amendment%20bill%20and%20the%20Kerala%20Cooperative%20Societies%20Amendment%20bill%20of%202022.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENone%20of%20the%20seven%20bills%20pertained%20to%20Centre-state%20relations%20and%20therefore%20did%20not%20require%20the%20assent%20of%20the%20President%2C%20Kerala%20maintained%20in%20its%20argument%20at%20the%20Court%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBarAndBench%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKerala%20challenges%20actions%20of%20governor%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Kerala%20government%20has%20also%20moved%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20against%20its%20governor%20Mohammmed%20Arif%20Khan%20for%20reserving%20the%20seven%20bills%20for%20the%20President%20when%20he%20could%20have%20dealt%20with%20them%20himself.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20state%20has%20argued%20in%20its%20petition%20that%20two%20of%20the%20seven%20bills%20remained%20with%20the%20governor%20for%20around%2024%20months%20before%20he%20passed%20it%20to%20the%20President%20for%20assent%3B%20the%20other%20five%20remained%20with%20the%20governor%20for%20between%20seven%20to%2016%20months.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKhan%E2%80%99s%20inaction%20regarding%20the%20bills%20has%20%E2%80%9Csubverted%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20legislature%20of%20the%20state%20and%20rendered%20its%20existence%20itself%20ineffective%20and%20otiose%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBarAndBench%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKerala%20has%20also%20alleged%20that%20the%20governor%20did%20not%20inform%20the%20President%20that%20the%20bills%20remained%20with%20him%20for%20so%20many%20months%2C%20pending%20assent.%20This%20amounts%20to%20a%20violation%20of%20Article%20200%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%2C%20as%20per%20which%20the%20governor%20has%20to%20send%20such%20bills%20to%20the%20President%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EApart%20from%20Kerala%2C%20states%20such%20as%20Punjab%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Telangana%20have%20raised%20similar%20concerns%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20about%20their%20governors.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711292099000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fkerala-moves-sc-against-president-murmu-for-withholding-assent-to-state-bills%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kerala%20has%20also%20moved%20the%20court%20against%20Governor%20Mohammed%20Arif%20Khan%20for%20keeping%20his%20assent%20on%20bills%20pending%20for%20months%20and%20then%20referring%20them%20to%20Murmu%20when%20there%20was%20no%20need%20to%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fkerala-moves-sc-against-president-murmu-for-withholding-assent-to-state-bills%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Ready%2C%20steady%2C%20eau!%20Waiters%20race%20returns%20to%20Paris%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711292026000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F2BD4%2Fproduction%2F_133002211_p0hlmf1x.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68649600%232%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20competition%20for%20waiters%20and%20waitresses%20began%20in%201914%2C%20but%20has%20not%20been%20held%20since%202011%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20sponsors.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A17%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fav%2Fworld-europe-68649600%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tata%20Neu%20changes%20its%20look%20with%20a%20new%20UI%2C%20eyes%20online%20food%20delivery%20foray%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711291480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-03%2F24%2Ffull%2F1711285241-6601.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftata-neu-changes-its-look-with-a-new-ui-eyes-online-food-delivery-foray-124032400436_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Source%20in%20the%20know%20also%20said%20that%20the%20firm%20is%20likely%20to%20roll-out%20its%20food%20delivery%20services%20during%20the%20ongoing%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftata-neu-changes-its-look-with-a-new-ui-eyes-online-food-delivery-foray-124032400436_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftata-neu-changes-its-look-with-a-new-ui-eyes-online-food-delivery-foray-124032400436_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftata-neu-changes-its-look-with-a-new-ui-eyes-online-food-delivery-foray-124032400436_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%20opens%20up%20about%20his%20comeback%20post-January%206%20riots%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711291417000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108753237%2Cimgsize-1169038.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ffrom-setback-to-comeback-trump-opens-up-about-his-comeback-post-january-6-riots%2Farticleshow%2F108751896.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20WORLD%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ffrom-setback-to-comeback-trump-opens-up-about-his-comeback-post-january-6-riots%2Farticleshow%2F108751896.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Confident%20That%20Pakistan-Occupied%20Kashmir%20Will%20Merge%20With%20India%3A%20Minister%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDefence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20said%20that%20the%20people%20of%20Pakistan-Occupied%20Kashmir%20(PoK)%20are%20themselves%20raising%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20merger%20with%20India.%20He%20expressed%20confidence%20that%20the%20people%20of%20PoK%20will%20merge%20with%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20Pakistan%20Prime%20Minister%20Shehbaz%20Sharif's%20recent%20remarks%20about%20Kashmir%2C%20Rajnath%20Singh%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BCan%20they%20ever%20take%20Kashmir%3F%20They%20should%20be%20worried%20about%20Pakistan-Occupied%20Kashmir.%20I%20had%20said%20almost%20one%20and%20a%20half%20years%20ago%20that%20there%20will%20be%20no%20need%20for%20us%20to%20attack%20and%20occupy%20because%20a%20situation%20is%20developing%20there%20that%20people%20of%20PoK%20themselves%20are%20demanding%20merger%20with%20India.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20being%20asked%20whether%20the%20government%20was%20making%20any%20plan%2C%20he%20responded%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20will%20not%20say%20anything%20more%2C%20I%20should%20not.%20We%20are%20not%20going%20to%20attack%20any%20country.%20India%20has%20a%20character%20of%20never%20attacking%20any%20country%20in%20the%20world%2C%20nor%20has%20it%20occupied%20an%20inch%20of%20other's%20territory.%20But%20PoK%20was%20ours%2C%20PoK%20is%20ours%2C%20and%20I%20am%20confident%20that%20PoK%20will%20itself%20merge%20with%20India.%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20made%20the%20comments%20during%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatvnews.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Faap-ki-adalat-rajnath-singh-tells-rajat-sharma-no-need-to-attack-people-of-pok-they-themselves-want-merger-with-india-2024-03-23-922914%5C%22%3E'%3Cem%3EAAP%20ki%20Adalat'%3C%2Fem%3E%20programme%20on%20India%20TV%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20February%2C%20a%20political%20activist%20from%20Pakistan-occupied%20Kashmir%20(PoK)%2C%20Amjad%20Ayub%20Mirza%2C%20had%20claimed%20that%20the%20people%20in%20PoK%20are%20fed%20up%20with%20Pakistani%20occupation%20and%20they%20are%20now%20demanding%20merger%20with%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20video%20released%20by%20him%2C%20activist%20Mirza%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20people%20of%20PoK%20in%20the%20last%20few%20days%20have%20told%20me%20that%20they%20now%20demand%20to%20be%20merged%20into%20India%2C%20as%20they%20are%20officially%20their%20citizens%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20recent%20elections%20in%20Pakistan%20have%20just%20given%20us%20a%20fractured%20mandate.%20The%20upcoming%20elections%20will%20have%20a%20fruitful%20result%20for%20India%20but%20we%20the%20people%20of%20PoK%20ask%20that%2C%20for%20how%20long%20will%20we%20have%20to%20wait%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20Pakistan's%20oppression%20and%20get%20merged%20in%20India%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20PoK%20activist%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20stated%20that%20India%20has%20a%20character%20of%20never%20attacking%20any%20nation%20and%20not%20occupying%20anyone's%20land.%20However%2C%20he%20asserted%20that%20India%20will%20give%20a%20befitting%20response%20if%20its%20prestige%20is%20attacked%20by%20anyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20a%20possible%20scenario%20where%20China%20attacks%20India%2C%20Rajnath%20Singh%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BGod%20should%20give%20them%20the%20good%20sense%20not%20to%20commit%20such%20mistakes.%20India%20has%20a%20character%20of%20never%20attacking%20any%20country%2C%20but%20if%20any%20country%20attacks%20us%2C%20we%20do%20not%20spare%20them.%20But%20the%20truth%20is%20that%20if%20anyone%20asks%20us%2C%20we%20have%20good%20relations%20with%20all%20our%20neighbours.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20maintain%20ties%20but%20not%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20India's%20self-respect.%20But%20if%20any%20country%20attacks%20India's%20prestige%2C%20it%20has%20the%20power%20to%20give%20it%20a%20befitting%20reply.%20We%20want%20to%20have%20good%20relations%20with%20neighbours%20because%20Atal%20ji%20used%20to%20say%20that%20we%20should%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20we%20can%20change%20friends%20in%20life%20but%20neighbours%20never%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20underlined%20that%20India%20will%20tackle%20any%20threat%20that%20arises%20from%20China%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20country%20has%20become%20a%20powerful%20nation%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20being%20asked%20whether%20there%20was%20any%20threat%20from%20China%20now%2C%20the%20Defence%20Minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20tackle%20if%20any%20threat%20arises%2C%20what's%20there%20in%20it.%20But%2C%20we%20cannot%20sit%20holding%20our%20heads%20in%20hands%20thinking%20about%20the%20threat.%20If%20the%20threat%20arises%2C%20it%20will%20be%20tackled.%20India%20is%20no%20more%20a%20weak%20country.%20India%20has%20become%20a%20powerful%20country%20in%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20allegation%20that%20China%20has%20occupied%20nearly%202%2C000%20square%20kilometres%20of%20India's%20territory%2C%20he%20expressed%20sadness%20over%20his%20remarks%20and%20stated%20that%20he%20does%20not%20want%20to%20remind%20him%20about%20the%20activities%20China%20did%20in%201962.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20feeling%20really%20sad%20that%20he%20is%20questioning%20the%20valour%20of%20our%20jawans.%20He%20should%20not%20be%20making%20such%20remarks.%20How%20much%20territory%20was%20occupied%20by%20China%20in%201962%20and%20what%20activities%20have%20been%20done%20by%20China.%20I%20do%20not%20want%20to%20remind%20him%20and%20do%20not%20talk%20about%20it.%20Rest%20assured%2C%20today%2C%20we%20can%20say%20that%20we%20will%20not%20like%20to%20lose%20even%20an%20inch%20of%20our%20territory.%20I%20cannot%20disclose%20much%20about%20the%20details%20because%20India%20and%20China%20are%20engaged%20in%20talks%2C%20and%20the%20talks%20are%20going%20on%20in%20a%20right%20manner.%20Talks%20are%20going%20on%20in%20a%20cordial%20atmosphere.%20Otherwise%2C%20I%20would%20have%20disclosed%20more%20details.%20Please%20do%20not%20compel%20me%20to%20disclose%20more.%20I%20cannot%20disclose%20much.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20February%2C%20India%20and%20China%20held%20the%2021st%20round%20of%20Corps%20Commander%20level%20meeting%20on%20Monday%20at%20the%20Chushul-Moldo%20border%20to%20defuse%20tensions%20along%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20(LAC)%20in%20Eastern%20Ladakh%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20nations%20have%20been%20engaged%20in%20a%20standoff%20since%20April-May%202020%20over%20the%20transgressions%20by%20the%20Chinese%20Army%20in%20multiple%20areas%20including%20the%20Finger%20area%2C%20Galwan%20Valley%2C%20Ho