mes%20luck%20is%20more%20important%20than%20high-tech%20equipment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEveryone%20there%20had%20all%20this%20up-to-date%20kit%20and%20I%20bowled%20up%20with%20three%20old%20machines%2C%20and%20one%20of%20them%20packed%20in.%20It%20just%20goes%20to%20show%20that%20it%20doesn't%20really%20matter%20what%20equipment%20you%20use%2C%20if%20you%20are%20walking%20over%20the%20find%20and%20are%20alert%20enough%20to%20what%20might%20be%20lurking%20underneath%20the%20soil%2C%20that%20makes%20all%20the%20difference%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20nugget%20has%20an%20estimated%20worth%20of%20between%20%C2%A330%2C000%2C%20or%20%2438%2C000%2C%20and%20%C2%A340%2C000%2C%20or%20%2450%2C700%2C%20according%20to%20Mullock%20Jones%2C%20which%20is%20handling%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbid.mullocksauctions.co.uk%2Fauctions%2F8860%2Fsrmu10178%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20sale.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrock%20believes%20it%20is%20the%20biggest%20to%20be%20found%20on%20English%20soil%2C%20as%20the%20previous%20largest%20find%20weighed%2054%20grams%2C%20The%20Guardian%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EConnecting%20with%20history%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222205%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20person%20using%20a%20metal%20detector.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f9e21856f5190019fceea6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221360%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJose%20Luque%20Olmedo%20%2F%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAmateur%20metal%20detectorists%20have%20been%20active%20for%20decades%2C%20driven%20by%20a%20hope%20to%20find%20valuable%20treasures%20or%20historical%20artifacts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20hobby%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2021%2F05%2F31%2Fstyle%2Fmetal-detectorists-ring-finders.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrowing%20in%20popularity%20in%20recent%20years%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20one%