Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chronline.com%2Fstories%2Ffamily-of-six-including-children-rescued-after-night-stranded-on-mount-hood%2C336892%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efamily%20used%20an%20iPhone%20feature%20to%20survive%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20they%20came%20lost%20in%20a%20freezing%20forest%20in%20Oregon%2C%20The%20Chronicle%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHigh%20altitude%20and%20bad%20weather%20conditions%20left%20the%20six-year-old%20family%20stranded%20in%20the%20Mt.%20Hood%20National%20Forest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20appears%20they%20were%20lost%20and%20unable%20to%20find%20their%20way%20back%20in%20the%20heavy%20snow%2C%20as%20well%20as%20experiencing%20the%20effects%20of%20fatigue%20and%20exposure%20due%20to%20the%20weather%20conditions%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Brian%20McCall%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20Clackamas%20County%20Sheriff's%20Office%2C%20per%20The%20Chronicle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20activated%20the%20Emergency%20SOS%20via%20satellite%20feature%20on%20their%20iPhone%20for%20help%2C%20and%20the%20Clackamas%20County%20Sheriff's%20Office%20received%20their%20distress%20signal%20at%207%3A30%20p.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Femergency-sos-iphone%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple's%20Emergency%20SOS%20feature%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Ev%3C%2Fspan%3Eia%20satellite%20debuted%20%3Cspan%3Ewith%20the%3C%2Fspan%3E%20iPhone%2014%3Cspan%3E%20model.%20It%20lets%20iPhone%2014%20and%2015%20owners%20contact%20emergency%20responders%20even%20when%20completely%20out%20of%20cell%20signal%20range.%20The%20connects%20you%20to%20satellites%20above%20the%20Earth%2C%20which%20will%20then%20relay%20your%20messages%20and%20location%20to%20responders%20nearby.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20had%20set%20off%20on%20Tuesday's%20hike%20from%20the%20Salmon%20River%20Trailhead.%20Eight%20miles%20and%203%2C500%20feet%20in%20elevation%20later%2C%20the%20group%2C%20which%20included%20two%20young%20children%2C%20found%20themselves%20battling%20adverse%20weather%20conditions%20and%20plummeting%20temperatures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGround%20crews%20were%20equipped%20with%20all-terrain%20vehicles%2C%20but%20it%20took%20a%20search-and-rescue%20team%20until%206%20a.m.%20the%20following%20morning%2C%20due%20to%20the%20snow%2C%20steep%20terrain%2C%20and%20fallen%20trees%2C%20to%20reach%20the%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20helicopter%20rescue%20attempt%20was%20unsuccessful%20due%20to%20the%20weather%20and%20terrain%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERescuers%20found%20the%20family%20cold%2C%20wet%2C%20and%20dehydrated%20but%20otherwise%20unharmed%2C%20and%20getting%20them%20back%20from%20the%20remote%20location%20also%20proved%20difficult.%20Another%20ground%20crew%2C%20using%20a%20Snowcat%20vehicle%2C%20departed%20at%2010%20a.m.%20and%20reached%20the%20family%20several%20hours%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20and%20rescuers%20were%20transported%20back%20to%20safety%2024%20hours%20after%20the%20initial%20SOS%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20easiest%20way%20to%20activate%20Apple's%20Emergency%20SOS%20feature%20is%20by%20holding%20the%20lock%20button%20and%20one%20of%20the%20volume%20buttons.%20When%20three%20sliders%20appear%2C%20you%20can%20swipe%20across%20the%20emergency%20call%20slider.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20has%20already%20been%20credited%20with%20saving%20many%20lives.%20It%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwpde.com%2Fnews%2Fnation-world%2Fwoman-dog-rescued-after-being-swept-up-to-200-feet-down-mary-jane-canyon-from-flash-flood-satellite-phone-sos-grandy-county-utah-moab-classic-air-medical%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20helped%20rescuers%20save%20a%20hiker%20and%20her%20dog%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20August%20after%20flood%20waters%20swept%20the%20pair%20down%20a%20Utah%20canyon.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20January%2C%20a%20student%20in%20Delaware%20was%20%3C