hich%20Won't%20Be%20Pressured%2C%20Will%20State%20Its%20Mind%3A%20S%20Jaishankar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EExternal%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20said%20on%20Sunday%20that%20%26quot%3Ba%20terrorist%20is%20a%20terrorist%26quot%3B%20in%20any%20language%20and%20one%20should%20not%20allow%20terrorism%20to%20be%20excused%20or%20defended%20because%20of%20a%20different%20explanation%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar's%20remarks%20came%20during%20his%20interaction%20with%20the%20Indian%20community%20members%20in%20Singapore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20a%20question%20on%20how%20Indian%20officials%20approach%20sensitive%20and%20linguistically%20different%20topics%20with%20their%20global%20counterparts%2C%20the%20minister%20said%20that%20in%20diplomacy%2C%20different%20countries%20bring%20their%20own%20cultures%2C%20traditions%20and%20sometimes%20their%20language%20or%20concepts%20to%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20also%20natural%20that%20there%20will%20be%20different%20viewpoints.%20And%20what%20diplomacy%20is%20about%20is%20to%20find%20a%20way%20of%20reconciling%20it%20and%20coming%20to%20some%20kind%20of%20agreement%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%20said%20however%20there%20are%20some%20issues%20when%20there%20is%20clarity%20and%20no%20confusion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiving%20the%20example%20of%20terrorism%2C%20he%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20take%20it%20in%20any%20language%2C%20but%20a%20terrorist%20is%20a%20terrorist%20in%20any%20language.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BNever%20allow%20something%20like%20terrorism%20to%20be%20excused%20or%20defended%20because%20they're%20using%20a%20different%20language%20or%20a%20different%20explanation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20without%20referring%20to%20any%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20there%20can%20be%20issues%20where%20two%20nations%20genuinely%20can%20have%20different%20viewpoints%20and%20there%20%26quot%3Bwill%20be%20issues%20when%20they%20are%20used%20as%20a%20cover%20as%20an%20excuse%20as%20a%20justification.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20one%20should%20be%20able%20to%20spot%20the%20difference%20and%20figure%20out%20a%20way%20how%20to%20deal%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20address%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20recapped%20India-Singapore%20relations%20dating%20back%20to%20the%20independence%20struggling%20days%20when%20Subhas%20Chandra%20Bose%20established%20the%20Indian%20National%20Army%20and%20made%20the%20'Delhi%20Chalo'%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20(Neta%3Cem%3E%20ji)%3C%2Fem%3E%20remains%20a%20visible%20inspiration%20for%20our%20entire%20nation%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said%20as%20he%20joined%20some%201%2C500%20Indian%20community%20members%20at%20the%20screening%20of%20the%20Singapore-made%20short%20film%20on%20Netaji.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20India%20has%20globalized%2C%20the%20two%20countries'%20relations%20that%20began%20as%20Look%20East%20policy%20and%20then%20on%20Act%20East%20policy...%20has%20gone%20on%20to%20India%20being%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20-%20the%20story%20in%20many%20ways%20actually%20began%20in%20Singapore%2C%20Jaishankar%20shared%20with%20the%20business-focused%20Indian%20community%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20more%20India%20globalizes%2C%20every%20aspect%20of%20that%20will%20be%20reflected%20in%20the%20intensity%20and%20quality%20of%20relationships%20with%20Singapore%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20underscored.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSingapore%20has%20been%20our%20partner%20in%20the%20globalization%20of%20India%20and%20that%20role%20and%20companionship%20is%20something%20that%20we%20value%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Jaishankar%2C%20who%20is%20on%20a%20three-day%20visit%20to%20the%20Asian%20financial%20hub.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%20also%20updated%20the%20Singapore-based%20Indian%20community%20on%20the%20accelerated%20pace%20of%20infrastructure%20development%20in%20India%20and%20highlighted%20%26quot%3BBharat%20being%20a%20global%20friend%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20India%20which%20will%20not%20be%20pressured%2C%20which%20will%20state%20its%20mind.%20If%20it%20has%20to%20make%20a%20choice%2C%20we%20will%20make%20a%20choice%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20our%20citizens%20...%20So%2C%20the%20idea%20is%20of%20much%20stronger%2C%20more%20capable%20India%20and%20willing%20to%20take%20the%20tough%20course%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%20assured%20that%20this%20is%20an%20India%20which%20looks%20after%20its%20citizens%20and%20people%20of%20Indian%20origins.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20more%20and%20more%20Indians%20settle%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20world%2C%20it%20is%20our%20responsibility%20to%20secure%20them%2C%20to%20ensure%20their%20wellbeing%20if%20they%20are%20in%20a%20difficult%20stage%2C%20to%20bring%20them%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Ukraine%20and%20Sudan%20were%20cited%20as%20examples%20of%20where%20Indians%20were%20caught%20between%20the%20wars%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20capable%20India%2C%20the%20diplomatic%20India%2C%20the%20reformed%20India%2C%20the%20protective%20India...%20in%20many%20ways%20the%20innovative%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20stressed%2C%20pointing%20to%20the%20global%20respect%20won%20by%20the%20Chandrayan%20landing%20on%20the%20Moon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20also%20India%2C%20which%20is%20a%20friend%20of%20the%20world.%20%26quot%3BFriendships%20begets%20more%20friendship%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20pointing%20to%20the%20supply%20of%20vaccines%20to%20nearly%20100%20countries%20during%20Covid-19.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20we%20step%20forward%20at%20times%20of%20difficulties%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jaishankar%2C%20adding%20that%20India%20gave%20a%20package%20of%20USD%204.5%20billion%20to%20Sri%20Lanka%20during%20the%20island%20state's%20economic%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAcross%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20today%2C%20if%20there%20is%20a%20problem%