%20have%20allegedly%20pointed%20to%20the%20transfer%20of%20land%20involving%20people%20of%20different%20religions%20%E2%80%9Cby%20fraudulent%20means.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVested%20interests%20can%20thus%20create%20communal%20conflict%20with%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20ahead%2C%20the%20notification%20claims%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20notification%20however%20adds%20that%20if%20a%20district%20commissioner%20notes%20that%20a%20no-objection%20certificate%20is%20%E2%80%9Cabsolutely%20necessary%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cwill%20not%20lead%20to%20any%20breach%20of%20law%20and%20order%2C%E2%80%9D%20then%20it%20can%20be%20issued%20with%20prior%20concurrence%20of%20the%20Assam%20Inspector%20General%20of%20Registration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20notification%20is%20signed%20by%20Gyanendra%20Dev%20Tripathi%2C%20the%20Principal%20Secretary%20to%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20Revenue%20Department.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELok%20Sabha%20elections%20in%2014%20constituencies%20in%20Assam%20will%20be%20conducted%20in%20three%20phases%2C%20on%20April%2019%2C%20April%2026%2C%20and%20May%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20notification%20follows%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20third%20phase%20of%20the%20Himanta%20government%E2%80%99s%20flagship%20Mission%20Basundhara%20under%20which%20only%20%E2%80%9Cindigenous%E2%80%9D%20people%20of%20Assam%20can%20apply%20to%20get%20land%20titles%20for%20government-owned%20lands.%20Himanta%20had%20earlier%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fislamphobia-statecraft-assam-himanta-biswa-sarma%5C%22%3Enoted%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Bengali-origin%20Muslims%20who%20are%20landless%20could%20not%20apply%20for%20land%20under%20this%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711283425000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F23221556%2F2022_11img23_Nov_2022_PTI11_23_2022_000240B.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fassam-pauses-noc-for-s