C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAmericans%20waiting%20for%20the%20housing%20affordability%20crisis%20to%20ease%20might%20be%20waiting%20a%20long%20time%2C%20even%20with%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20proposals%20to%20open%20up%20the%20market%20to%20more%20Americans%2C%20real%20estate%20experts%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20not%20to%20say%20Biden's%20list%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiden-sotu-housing-affordability-stimulus-buyers-sellers-mortgage-credits-supply-2024-3%5C%22%3Eproposals%20to%20lower%20housing%20costs%3C%2Fa%3E%20won't%20have%20an%20impact%2C%20according%20to%20Daryl%20Fairweather%2C%20the%20chief%20economist%20of%20the%20real%20estate%20listings%20site%20Redfin.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20some%20ideas%20%E2%80%94%20like%20tax%20credits%20for%20first-time%20buyers%20%E2%80%94%20do%20little%20to%20tackle%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhousing-market-outlook-shortage-home-prices-mortgage-rates-real-estate-2024-1%5C%22%3Ehousing%20shortage%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20may%20end%20up%20stimulating%20more%20demand.%20That%20means%20any%20relief%20is%20unlikely%20to%20come%20in%20the%20form%20of%20bringing%20down%20sky-high%20prices.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20effect%20on%20the%20housing%20affordability%20crisis%20is%20going%20to%20be%20muted.%20It's%20not%20going%20to%20be%20noticeable%20even%20in%20the%20long%20run%2C%26quot%3B%20Fairweather%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELow%20housing%20inventory%20is%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20affordability%20issue.%20A%20lack%20of%20new%20construction%20of%20single-family%20homes%20since%20the%20financial%20crisis%20combined%20with%20the%20%26quot%3Block-in%26quot%3B%20effect%20of%20existing%20homeowners%20staying%20put%20to%20hold%20on%20to%20their%20low%20mortgage%20rate%20has%20created%20a%20big%20supply-demand%20imbalance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20Biden's%20housing%20affordability%20measures%20would%20fuel%20demand%20further%20at%20a%20time%20when%20supply%20is%20still%20historically%20tight%2C%20according%20to%20Lawrence%20Yun%2C%20the%20chief%20economist%20of%20NAR.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20president's%20initiatives%20could%20help%20lower-income%20families%20get%20into%20the%20housing%20market%2C%20it%20could%20also%20exacerbate%20the%20supply-demand%20imbalance%2C%20putting%20upwards%20pressure%20on%20home%20prices%20overall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20current%20situation%20is%20really%20about%20supply%2C%26quot%3B%20Yun%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EAddressing%20a%20dearth%20of%20housing%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Fairweather%2C%20the%20only%20initiatives%20that%20will%20make%20a%20long-lasting%20difference%20in%20home%20affordability%20are%20Biden's%20efforts%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhousing-market-outlook-forecast-mortgage-rates-homebuilding-inventory-prices-2024-2023-12%5C%22%3Ebuild%20more%20houses%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20President%20is%20pushing%20for%20Congress%20to%20pass%20legislation%20to%20build%20or%20renovate%20around%202%20million%20homes%2C%20which%20would%20help%20alleviate%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-housing-market-outlook-inventory-supply-new-listings-home-prices-2024-3%5C%22%3Elack%20of%20inventory%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEstimates%20of%20America's%20housing%20shortage%20range%20from%203%20million%20homes%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2023%2F03%2F08%2Fhomes%2Fhousing-shortage%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eas%20many%20as%206%20million%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Biden%20administration%20is%20also%20offering%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiden-pay-homeowners-sell-house-starter-tax-credit-housing-shortage-2024-3%5C%22%3Eone-year%20%2410%2C000%20tax%20credit%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20homeowners%20who%20are%20willing%20to%20sell%2C%20which%20could%20unlock%20housing%20supply%20from%20those%20who%20own%20multiple%20properties%2C%20Fairweather%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20what's%20really%20needed%20is%20new%20supply%2C%20and%20building%20enough%20homes%20to%20make%20housing%20more%20affordable%20is%20a%20huge%20task%20in%20America.%20Yun%20estimated%20that%20it%20could%20take%20at%20least%20three%20to%20four%20years%20of%20building%20for%20supply%20and%20demand%20to%20balance%20out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFairweather%20thinks%20it%20could%20take%20around%20a%20decade%20to%20build%20Biden's%20proposed%202%20million%20homes.%20Building%20in%20America%20is%20difficult%2C%20and%20construction%20is%20often%20governed%20by%20a%20patchwork%20of%20local%20and%20state%20rules%20that%20make%20it%20hard%20for%20developers%20to%20break%20ground.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBiden%20has%20his%20plan%2C%20which%20is%20to%20pump%20money%20into%20the%20system.%20But%20the%20problem%20with%20the%20housing%20market%20isn't%20really%20that%20there%20isn't%20enough%20money%20going%20toward%20housing.%20It's%20more%20the%20red%20tape%20and%20the%20local%20opposition%20that%20has%20been%20the%20biggest%20barrier%20to%20building%20housing%2C%26quot%3B%20Fairweather%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20once%20that%20supply%20is%20added%2C%20the%20effect%20on%20home%20prices%20could%20still%20be%20muted.%20That's%20because%20the%20country%20is%20already%20deep%20in%20a%20housing%20shortage%2C%20Yun%20said%2C%20and%20it%20will%20take%20years%20for%20supply%20to%20catch%20up%20with%20demand%2C%20let%20alone%20have%20demand%20exceed%20supply%2C%20which%20is%20what%20would%20cause%20prices%20to%20drop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20will%20not%20come%20down%20in%20any%20meaningful%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20Yun%20said%20of%20home%20prices.%20%26quot%3BMaybe%20there's%20a%20single-digit%20price%20adjustment%20temporarily%2C%20but%20any%20meaningful%20%5Bdecline%5D%20is%20not%20going%20to%20happen%20%E2%80%A6%20So%20for%20anyone%20who's%20just%20waiting%20and%20waiting%2C%20well%2C%20that%20time%20will%20be%20long.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20upside%20is%20that%20prices%20aren't%20likely%20to%20rise%20much%20more.%20Yun%20thinks%20home%20prices%20will%20stay%20around%20their%20current%20level%20for%20the%20next%20three%20years%20before%20more%20supply%20finally%20makes%20its%20way%20to%20buyers.%20Then%2C%20assuming%20supply%20catches%20up%20with%20demand%2C%20the%20growth%20of%20home%20prices%20will%20likely%20slow%20in%20line%20with%20people's%20growing%20incomes%2C%20meaning%20housing%20will%20feel%20more%20affordable%2C%20even%20as%20actual%20prices%20don't%20see%20much%20of%20a%20change%2C%20he%20predicted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffred.stlouisfed.org%2Fseries%2FMSPUS%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emedian%20sale%20price%20of%20a%20home%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20US%20clocked%20in%20at%20%24417%2C000%20in%20the%20fourth%20quarter%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20the%20Department%20of%20Housing%20and%20Urban%20Development.%20That's%20a%2027%25%20increase%20from%20how%20much%20homes%20cost%20prior%20to%20the%20pandemic%2C%20with%20the%20median%20sales%20price%20clocking%20in%20at%20%24327%2C100%20in%20the%20fourth%20quarter%20of%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.redfin.com%2Fus-housing-market%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHome%20prices%20were%20already%20up%206.5%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20year-over-year%20in%20February%2C%20according%20to%20Redfin%20data.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhousing-market-affordability-homebuyer-earnings-income-price-trends-covid-comparison-2024-2%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20an%20analysis%20by%20Zillow%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20homebuyers%20need%20to%20earn%2080%25%20more%20than%20they%20did%20before%20the%20pandemic%20to%20afford%20a%20home%20in%202024.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fw