ts%20of%20jungle%20operations.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDecades%20of%20desert%20ops%20have%20dulled%20jungle%20warfare%20skills%2C%20requiring%20more%20specialized%20training%20in%20this%20environment.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20spending%20more%20than%2020%20years%20fighting%20in%20the%20wars%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20US%20special%20operators%20are%20pivoting%20to%20other%20environments.%20With%20the%20potential%20for%20a%20conflict%20with%20China%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20looming%20ever%20larger%20in%20the%20background%2C%20the%20US%20special%20operations%20community%20is%20focusing%20more%20and%20more%20on%20jungle%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20relatively%20recent%20exercise%20involving%20Marine%20Raiders%20highlighted%20the%20challenges%20and%20unique%20requirements%20of%20jungle%20warfare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFrom%20the%20desert%20to%20the%20jungle%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20summer%2C%20a%20small%20team%20of%20Marine%20Raiders%20completed%20a%20jungle%20warfare%20course%20that%20addresses%20the%20challenges%20US%20forces%20might%20encounter%20in%20an%20Indo-Pacific%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETaught%20by%20special%20operations%20and%20law%20enforcement%20veterans%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fttoscorp.com%2Fjungle-training%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETactical%20Tracking%20Operations%20School%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20course%20began%20in%202015%20but%20really%20took%20off%20in%202021.%20The%20two-week%20course%20takes%20place%20on%20the%20island%20of%20Oahu%2C%20Hawaii%2C%20and%20is%20designed%20to%20take%20small%20special%20operations%20teams%20and%20teach%20them%20the%20necessary%20skills%20to%20survive%20and%20thrive%20in%20jungle%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Marine%20Raiders%20trained%20in%20jungle%20mobility%20skills%2C%20such%20as%20navigating%20thick%20brush%2C%20scaling%20and%20rappelling%20cliffs%2C%20and%20traversing%20rivers%2C%20counter%20Improvised%20Explosive%20Device%20(IED)%20techniques%2C%20reaction%20to%20contact%2C%20and%20ambushes.%20Throughout%20the%20course%2C%20the%20special%20operators%20either%20tracked%20an%20adversary%20or%20prevented%20them%20from%20tracking%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLooking%20at%20the%20Pacific%20and%20deployments%20in%20that%20region%2C%20learning%20these%20skills%20is%20essential%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Marine%20Raider%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsof.news%2Fmarsoc%2Fmarsoc-jungle-training%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epress%20release%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BFor%20so%20long%20we%20trained%20for%20desert%20environments%20and%20now%20we%20have%20to%20look%20at%20where%20we%20could%20be%20needed%20next%2C%20and%20the%20jungle%20is%20top%20of%20that%20list.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221406%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Marine%20Raider%20with%20Marine%20Forces%20Special%20Operations%20Command%20traverses%20a%20river%20during%20a%20jungle%20mobility%20course%2C%20Aug.%204%2C%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65fd76d9895d822030333899%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22943%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Marine%20Raider%20with%20Marine%20Forces%20Special%20Operations%20Command%20traverses%20a%20river%20during%20a%20jungle%20mobility%20course%2C%20Aug.%204%2C%202023.%3Cp%3EU.S.%20Marine%20Corps%20photo%20by%20Cpl.%20Henry%20Rodriguez%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20course%20ends%20with%20a%20final%20exercise%20that%20lasts%20up%20to%20three%20days%20and%20tests%20all%20the%20skillsets%20taught.%20After%20a%20simulated%20ambush%2C%20the%20students%20must%20regroup%20and%20hunt%20down%20the%20adversary%20using%20their%20tracking%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20decades%20of%20counterterrorism%20and%20counterinsurgency%20operations%20in%20Iraq%2C%20Afghanistan%2C%20and%20Syria%20largely%20dulled%20the%20jungle%20warfare%20capabilities%20of%20many%20units.%20Jungle%20warfare%20presents%20a%20whole%20different%20level%20of%20difficulty%20and%20requires%20specialized%20training%20to%20operate%20effectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20same%20problems%20that%20we%20have%20now%3A%20low%20visibility%2C%20difficulty%20for%20intelligence%2C%20surveillance%20and%20reconnaissance%20platforms%2C%20broken%20communications%2C%20and%20logistical%20issues%2C%20they%20all%20existed%20for%20troops%20during%20WWII%20and%20Vietnam%2C%26quot%3B%20Cody%20Carroll%2C%20the%20vice%20president%20of%20the%20school%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20didn't%20need%20to%20reinvent%20the%20wheel%2C%20just%20build%20the%20skills%20that%20we%20stopped%20training%20because%20we%20spent%2020%20years%20in%20the%20desert.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221407%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Marine%20Raider%20with%20Marine%20Forces%20Special%20Operations%20Command%20navigates%20a%20single%20rope%20bridge%20during%20a%20jungle%20mobility%20course%2C%20Aug.%204%2C%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65fd77552417f97b87ce53ea%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22937%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Marine%20Raider%20with%20Marine%20Forces%20Special%20Operations%20Command%20navigates%20a%20single%20rope%20bridge%20during%20a%20jungle%20mobility%20course%2C%20Aug.%204%2C%202023.%3Cp%3EU.S.%20Marine%20Corps%20photo%20by%20Cpl.%20Henry%20Rodriguez%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20movement%20in%20the%20jungle%20is%20much%20more%20restricted%20and%20visibility%20is%20often%20limited%20to%20just%20a%20few%20yards.%20Moreover%2C%20there%20are%20many%20small%20and%20large%20animals%20that%20can%20ruin%20someone's%20day%2C%20necessitating%20the%20right%20survival%20training.%20Tracking%20is%20another%20important%20part%20of%20jungle%20operations.%20With%20so%20much%20foliage%2C%20it's%20easy%20for%20an%20untrained%20unit%20to%20leave%20evidence%20of%20its%20direction%20in%20the%20jungle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI