20response%20might%20be%20placed%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20history%20of%20Zionism.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpecifically%2C%20Theodor%20Herzl%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20abandon%20his%20liberal%20Hungarian%20nationalism%20%E2%80%93%20upon%20realising%20this%20identity%20would%20soon%20be%20overwhelmed%20by%20the%20new%20European%20ethnic%20nationalisms%2C%20which%2C%20having%20gained%20currency%20after%20the%20failure%20of%20the%20revolutions%20of%201848%2C%20would%20eventually%20make%20all%20Europe%20unsafe%20for%20the%20Jews.%20And%20then%2C%20I%20should%20suggest%2C%20to%20seek%20to%20defend%20the%20Jewish%20peoples%20of%20Europe%20from%20ethnic%20nationalism%2C%20by%20inventing%20his%20Zionism%20as%20yet%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eanother%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20accommodating%20thereby%20the%20inherently%20anti-Semitic%20claim%20that%20the%20Jewish%20people%20did%20not%20belong%20in%20the%20West%20but%20in%20Palestine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELong%20after%20his%20death%20this%20has%20enabled%20the%20West%20to%20minimise%20its%20responsibility%20for%20Shoah.%20Today%2C%20when%20Israel%20bombs%20Gaza%2C%20it%20is%20in%20fact%20the%20West%20that%20does%20so.%20And%20the%20West%20it%20is%20that%20admonishes%20bewildered%20Palestinians%20as%20they%20die%2C%20%E2%80%9CNever%20again!%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%2C%20thereafter%2C%20in%20terrorising%20the%20Arab%20and%20the%20Muslim%20world%2C%20the%20West%20terrorises%20at%20the%20same%20time%20Israelis%2C%20placing%20them%20forever%20as%20anxious%20local%20gendarmerie%2C%20ever%20threatened%2C%20ever%20dependent%20on%20Western%20largesse%2C%20forever%20denied%20the%20possibility%20of%20real%20freedom.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAndrew%20Handler%2C%20wartime%20member%20of%20the%20Zionist%20youth%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMaccabi%20ha-Za%E2%80%99ir%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0has%20shown%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EDori%3A%20The%20Life%20%26amp%3B%20Times%20of%20Theodor%20Herzl%20in%20Budapest%201860-1878%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3EUniversity%20of%20Alabama%20Press%2C%201983)%20how%20the%20campaign%20for%20an%20ethnic%20Magyar-dominated%20Hungarian%20Kingdom%20had%20made%20up%20the%20lie%20that%20rule%20from%20Vienna%20had%20enabled%20the%20Jews%20to%20rob%20the%20Hungarian%20people.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYet%20this%20very%20anti-Semitism%20was%20to%20inspire%2C%20paradoxically%2C%20as%20Handler%20has%20argued%2C%20the%20Zionist%20programme%20itself.%20On%20June%2024%2C%201878%2C%20Gy%C5%91z%C5%91%C2%A0%C2%A0Ist%C3%B3czy%20set%20out%20in%20the%20Hungarian%20Diet%20that%20the%20Jews%20would%20destroy%20Hungary%20and%20the%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%9Csolution%C2%A0is%20none%20other%20than%20the%20restoration%20of%20the%20ancient%20Jewish%20state%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D.%20The%20Jewish%20Question%20was%20a%20national%20one%2C%20he%20said%2C%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eestablishment%20in%20Palestine%20of%20an%20independent%20Jewish%20state%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHandler%20points%20out%20the%20%E2%80%9Cstriking%20similarity%20between%20key%20passages%20of%20Istoczy%E2%80%99s%20anti-Semitic%20screed%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20Palesztina%20Beszcd%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0Herzl%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EDer%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EJudenstaat%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%20laying%20out%20the%20ideology%20of%20the%20future%20state%20of%20Israel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20Herzl%20decided%20that%20the%20Jewish%20peoples%20of%20Europe%20could%20only%20gain%20safety%20by%20creating%20their%20own%20ethnic%20nationalism%2C%20%26amp%3B%20so%20adopted%20the%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eanti-Semitic%20demand%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0that%20Palestine%20become%20the%20Jewish%20homeland.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYet%20Herzl%E2%80%99s%20Zionism%20%26amp%3B%20the%20policy%20to%20which%20it%20led%2C%20namely%20the%20Balfour%20Declaration%2C%20was%20opposed%20by%20liberal%20Western%20Jews%20such%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbalfourproject.org%2Fedwin-montagu-and-zionism-1917%5C%22%3EBritish%20statesman%20Edwin%20Montagu%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20wish%20to%20place%20on%20record%20my%20view%20that%20the%20policy%20of%20His%20Majesty%E2%80%99s%20Government%20is%20anti-Semitic%20and%20in%20result%20will%20prove%20a%20rallying%20ground%20for%20Anti-Semites%20in%20every%20country%20in%20the%20world%E2%80%A6I%20assert%20that%20there%20is%20not%20a%20Jewish%20nation%E2%80%A6When%20the%20Jews%20are%20told%20that%20Palestine%20is%20their%20national%20home%2C%20every%20country%20will%20immediately%20desire%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20its%20Jewish%20citizens%2C%20and%20you%20will%20find%20a%20population%20in%20Palestine%20driving%20out%20its%20present%20inhabitants%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENevertheless%2C%20the%20new%20ethnic%20nationalisms%20spread%20rapidly%2C%20each%20ethnic%20majority%20seeking%20to%20award%20itself%20a%20territory%20and%20the%20state%20that%20went%20with%20it%2C%20promoting%20mutually%20exclusive%20extravagant%20claims%20intolerant%20of%20those%20outside%20the%20mythical%20%E2%80%9Cnation%E2%80%9D%2C%20all%20seized%20by%20the%20identical%20Hobbesian%20paranoia%20about%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eoutsiders%20within.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ELook%20to%20India%20to%20see%20how%20this%20travelled%3A%20for%20Vinayak%20Damodar%20Savarkar%20who%20did%20much%20to%20shape%20the%20Indian%20ideology%20of%20today%20justified%20what%20Hitler%20was%20doing%20shortly%20before%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EKristallnacht%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ESeveral%20communities%20may%20live%20in%20one%20country%20for%20thousands%20of%20years%20but%20this%20does%20not%20help%20in%20forming%20a%20nation%E2%80%A6In%20Germany%20the%20movement%20of%20the%20Germans%20is%20the%20national%20movement%20but%20that%20of%20the%20Jews%20is%20a%20communal%20one.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESavarkar%E2%80%99s%20speech%20was%C2%A0reported%C2%A0in%20the%20weekly%20confidential%20(Intelligence)%20report%20to%20the%20District%20Magistrate%20Poona%2C%20October%201938%C2%A0.%20He%20then%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20elaborated%20on%20this%20to%20students%20of%20the%20Law%20College%2C%20Poona%20in%20July%201939%2C%20before%20hostilities%20commenced%20in%20World%20War%20II%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%9CNationality%20did%20not%20depend%20so%20much%20on%20a%20common%20geographical%20area%20as%20on%20unity%20of%20thought%2C%20religion%2C%20language%20and%20culture.%20For%20this%20reason%20the%20Germans%20and%20Jews%20could%20not%20be%20regarded%20as%20one%20nation.%20%3Cem%3EIn%20the%20same%20way%20India%20was%20a%20nation%20of%20Hindus%20as%20they%20were%20in%20the%20majority%3C%2Fem%3E%20(emphasis%20added%2C%20Bombay%20Province%20Weekly%20Letter%2C%20No.%2020%2C%20September%2030%2C%201939).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EAuthoritarian%20variants%20produced%20distinct%20European%20fascisms%3A%20although%20Germany%20is%20the%20most%20cited%2C%20we%20might%20look%20to%20France%2C%20turning%20in%20on%20itself%20after%20defeat%20at%20Sedan%20and%20the%20Paris%20Commune%20to%20look%20for%20an%20%E2%80%9Cenemy%20within%E2%80%9D%20when%20it%20persecuted%20Alfred%20Dreyfus.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20that%20falsehood%20being%20exposed%2C%20anti-Semitism%20persisted%2C%20fortified%20by%20the%20colonial%20racism%20common%20to%20most%20European%20states%3B%20so%20years%20later%20it%20powered%20popular%20support%20for%20Petain%20%26amp%3B%20his%20Vichy%20collaboration%20with%20National%20Socialism%2C%20which%20rounded%20up%20Jews%20to%20send%20them%20off%20to%20be%20tortured%20and%20murdered%2C%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ERafle%20du%20Vel%E2%80%99%20d%E2%80%99Hiv%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eat%20the%20cycling%20stadium%20in%20Paris%20in%20July%201942.%20Maurice%20Papon%2C%20one%20of%20its%20high%20functionaries%2C%20was%20like%20most%20never%20punished%3B%20accordingly%2C%20he%20was%20to%20go%20on%20to%20torture%20Algerians%20and%20detain%20them%20in%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Esame%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20stadium%20in%20Paris%20in%201961%20and%20organise%20their%20murder.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Insufficiently%20acknowledged%2C%20this%20very%20anti-Semitism%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ereborn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20today%20as%20Islamophobia%2C%20serving%20to%20appease%20both%20traditional%20anti-Semites%20as%20well%20as%20survivors%20of%20genocide.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20such%20French%20tradition%20that%20accounts%20for%20the%20surreal%20spectacle%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20Sephardic%C2%A0%C3%89ric%20Zemmour%C2%A0reassuring%20the%20French%20that%20their%20ancestors%20had%20no%20responsibility%20for%20Shoah%2C%20even%20as%20his%20fellow%20right%20wing%20colleague%20Marine%20Le%20Pen%20supports%20Israel%20yet%20is%20silent%20on%20her%20own%20family%E2%80%99s%20rich%20anti-Semitic%20history%3B%20as%20well%20as%20the%20absurdity%20of%20how%20the%20%E2%80%9Chijab%20question%E2%80%9D%20has%20now%20become%20the%20central%20concern%20of%20French%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ela%C3%AFcit%C3%A9%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20rapidly%20o%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eccidentalising%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20Jews%20whom%20it%20so%20recently%20orientalised%2C%20and%20orientalising%20instead%20Muslims%2C%20consistent%20with%20the%20creation%20of%20%E2%80%9Canti-Semitism%E2%80%9D%20as%20a%20matter%20of%20concern%20as%20entirely%20distinct%20from%20other%20racism.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMight%20we%20not%20therefore%20see%20Zionism%20itself%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Enot%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20as%20a%20lobby%20that%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20impedes%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20US%20strategic%20concerns%2C%20but%20a%20subordinate%20agent%20that%20enacts%20them%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Elimiting%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20thereby%20its%20own%20agency%3F%20We%20might%20recall%20that%20during%20the%20Suez%20Crisis%20the%20British%20MP%20Nye%20Bevan%20had%20focused%20on%20those%20responsible%20for%20the%20debacle%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20complain%20about%20the%20tune%2C%20there%20is%20no%20reason%20to%20criticise%20the%20monkey%20when%20the%20organ-grinder%20is%20present%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(House%20of%20Commons%20Debates%2C%20May%2016%2C%201957)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%C2%A0%20it%20is%20not%20%E2%80%9CJewish%20control%20of%20the%20media%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20that%20conspiratorial%20anti-Semitic%20fantasy%20that%20serves%20some%20as%20well%20as%20Islamophobia%20%E2%80%93%20but%20Western%20policy%2C%20specifically%20American%2C%20which%20defines%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EIsrael%E2%80%99s%20role%20in%20safeguarding%20its%20interest%20in%20controlling%20petroleum%20and%C2%A0%20international%20waterways%2C%20which%20accounts%20for%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20acts%20today.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EKannan%20Srinivasan%20is%20at%20Wertheim%20Study%20New%20York%20Public%20Library%20and%20can%20be%20reached%20at%20kannansrinivasan%40icloud.com.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3ESrinivasan%20is%20grateful%20for%20inspiration%20from%20Catherine%20Benoit%2C%20Akeel%20B