%2Findia-bloc-to-hold-maha-rally-on-march-31-to-safeguard-democracy-gopal-rai-124032400218_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sara%3A%20Wants%20to%20star%20in%20all%20Ranveer's%20films%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711276263000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108749635%2Cimgsize-60006.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsara-ali-khan-reveals-the-rumour-she-wants-to-start-about-herself-wants-to-star-in-all-ranveer-singhs-films%2Farticleshow%2F108749635.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108749635.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ESara%20Ali%20Khan%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20receiving%20praise%20for%20her%20performance%20in%20her%20latest%20release%2C%20'Ae%20Watan%20Mere%20Watan'%2C%20recently%20engaged%20in%20a%20candid%20rapid-fire%20round%20during%20a%20recent%20interview%20with%20a%20media%20house.%20When%20questioned%20about%20her%20dating%20history%20with%20a%20co-actor%2C%20the%20actress%20responded%20with%20refreshing%20honesty%2C%20affirming%20a%20simple%20%26quot%3Byes.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsara-ali-khan-reveals-the-rumour-she-wants-to-start-about-herself-wants-to-star-in-all-ranveer-singhs-films%2Farticleshow%2F108749635.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Couples%20who%20will%20celebrate%20their%20first%20Holi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711276200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108750540%2Cimgsize-64952.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fholi-2024-bollywood-celebrity-couples-who-will-celebrate-their-first-holi%2Fphotostory%2F108750540.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108750540.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fholi-2024-bollywood-celebrity-couples-who-will-celebrate-their-first-holi%2Fphotostory%2F108750540.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Where%20Are%20the%20'Don%20Quixotes'%20of%20Indian%20Academia%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2F29112534%2Fcensorship.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20almost%20two%20years%E2%80%A6%20again%20I%20got%20blessed%20with%20the%20mercy%20(from%20whom%2C%20you%20guess).%20This%20is%20the%20third%20time%20in%20the%20last%206%20years%20that%20I%20am%20leaving%20my%20job.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20morning%20began%20with%20this%20message%20from%20Mukesh%20Kumar%2C%20a%20friend%20and%20journalist.%20Kumar%20was%20a%20teacher%20and%20dean%20in%20the%20media%20and%20communication%20department%20of%20Lovely%20University%20in%20Jalandhar%20for%20about%20two%20years.%20Yesterday%2C%20he%20resigned%20from%20his%20job.%20Or%20was%20made%20to%20resign.%20His%20employer%2C%20the%20university%2C%20felt%20that%20his%20presence%20on%20the%20campus%20was%20harmful%20to%20its%20interests%20and%20he%20should%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20third%20job%20he%20has%20had%20to%20leave%20in%20these%20last%206%20years%2C%20said%20Kumar.%20Before%20Lovely%20University%2C%20he%20had%20been%20removed%20from%20Shri%20Guru%20Gobind%20Singh%20Tricentenary%20University%20(SGT%20University)%2C%20Gurgaon%20and%20Makhanlal%20Chaturvedi%20Journalism%20University%2C%20Bhopal.%20It%20is%20not%20very%20difficult%20to%20understand%20why%20he%20had%20to%20leave%20these%20institutions.%20Kumar%20dislikes%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20and%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cmark%3E%3C%2Fmark%3EKumar%20is%20a%20face%20well%20recognised%20by%20Hindi-speaking%20viewers.%20Everyone%20remembers%20his%20literary%20discussion%20%E2%80%98Subah%20Savere%E2%80%99%20with%20Namvar%20Singh%20on%20Doordarshan.%20The%20talk%20shows%20and%20discussions%20he%20conducts%20on%20contemporary%20political%20and%20social%20issues%20on%20the%20platform%20of%20%E2%80%98Satya%20Hindi%E2%80%99%20are%20very%20popular.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKumar%20talks%20calmly.%20But%20he%20has%20firm%20secular%20and%20democratic%20values.%20It%20becomes%20natural%20then%20for%20a%20person%20like%20him%20to%20be%20critical%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20RSS.%20He%20does%20not%20pretend%20to%20be%20impartial%2C%20which%20is%20what%20many%20journalists%20claim%20to%20be%20when%20they%20tolerate%20the%20majoritarian%20ideology%20of%20the%20BJP%20or%20the%20RSS.%20They%20claim%20that%20they%20do%20not%20take%20sides%20between%20secularism%20and%20communalism.%20They%20have%20a%20duty%20to%20only%20report%20the%20battle%20between%20these%20two%20ideologies.%20It%20is%20as%20if%20they%20are%20reporting%20a%20wrestling%20match%20where%20they%20are%20mere%20observers.%20Kumar%20does%20not%20belong%20to%20this%20league%20of%20journalists.%20One%20can%20understand%20that%20a%20journalist%20should%20not%20be%20biased%20in%20favour%20of%20any%20political%20party%20in%20his%20journalism%20but%20he%20must%20be%20partisan%20towards%20the%20values%20of%20civility%20and%20refinement.%20Otherwise%2C%20why%20pursue%20journalism%20at%20all%3F%20And%20we%20know%20that%20the%20ideology%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20RSS%20is%20opposed%20to%20civility%20or%20refinement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20considers%20journalists%20like%20Kumar%20as%20its%20enemies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Lovely%20University%20invited%20him%2C%20it%20knew%20his%20history.%20The%20institute%20was%20also%20familiar%20with%20his%20views.%20Being%20secular%2C%20you%20will%20definitely%20be%20an%20opponent%20or%20critic%20of%20BJP%20or%20RSS.%20Aware%20of%20all%20this%2C%20Lovely%20University%20chose%20to%C2%A0%20invite%20him%20as%20a%20faculty%20member.%20Why%20did%20it%20then%20ask%20him%20to%20go%20now%3F%20Or%20will%20it%20say%20that%20he%20left%20voluntarily%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20coming%20to%20the%20university%2C%20Kumar%20had%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20he%20would%20not%20leave%20his%20journalism.%20He%20would%20not%20stop%20his%20talk%20shows.%20The%20management%20had%20no%20objection%20to%20his%20condition.%20Why%20did%20it%20now%20ask%20him%20to%20stop%20his%20shows%20to%20be%20able%20to%C2%A0%20continue%20in%20the%20university%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20difficult%20to%20understand%20the%20reason%20why%20it%20happened%20now.%20Elections%20are%20close%20and%20BJP%20wants%20to%20silence%20all%20its%20critics.%20Lovely%20University%20cannot%20afford%20enmity%20with%20BJP%20at%20this%20stage.%20Its%20patron%20is%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20from%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP).%20They%20know%20how%20heavy%20the%20cost%20of%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20anger%20can%20be%20for%20them.%20What%20do%20they%20lose%20if%20they%20sacrifice%20Kumar%20for%20their%20safety%3F%20After%20all%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20we%20remember%20what%20Ashoka%20University%20did%20to%20Pratap%20Bhanu%20Mehta%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20there%20is%20only%20one%20condition%20for%20the%20survival%20of%20institutions%3A%20declaration%20of%20loyalty%20to%20the%20BJP%20government.%20If%20you%20do%20not%20do%20it%20then%2C%20at%20the%20very%20least%2C%20you%20should%20be%20silent.%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20outspokenness%20could%20have%20been%20dangerous%20for%20the%20administrators%20of%20Lovely%20University.%20He%20faced%20a%20choice%3A%20stop%20his%20program%20and%20remain%20at%20the%20university%2C%20or%20continue%20speaking%20and%20lose%20the%20job.%20Kumar%20chose%20his%20voice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20choice%20is%20bound%20to%20cause%20economic%20insecurity%20to%20him.%20But%20what%20should%20one%20do%20when%20asked%20to%20choose%20between%20freedom%20and%20security%3F%20Kumar%20has%20answered%20it.%20He%20remains%20what%20he%20was.%20Unlike%20him%2C%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20Lovely%20University%20lost%20its%20right%20to%20be%20called%20a%20university%3F%20It%20can%20be%20said%20that%20the%20presence%20or%20absence%20of%20one%20person%20does%20not%20make%20much%20difference%20to%20any%20institution.%20But%20the%20reason%20for%20which%20he%20had%20to%20leave%20tells%20us%20whether%20the%20university%20is%20able%20to%20fulfil%20its%20dharma%20or%20not.%20That%20dharma%20is%20to%20provide%20and%20create%20open%20space%20for%20free%20thoughts.%20If%20the%20university%20prevents%20you%20from%20expressing%20your%20views%20publicly%2C%20then%20it%20is%20defeating%20its%20purpose.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20important%20to%20reiterate%20that%20one%20of%20the%20tasks%20of%20academics%20is%20to%20constantly%20communicate%20with%20society%20so%20that%20it%20can%20understand%20itself%20better%20and%20also%20think%20about%20and%20what%20is%20happening%20to%20it.%20Teachers%20provide%20society%20with%20facts%20and%20also%20make%20available%20conceptual%20tools%2C%20with%20the%20help%20of%20which%20it%20can%20analyse%20events%20and%20situations.%20This%20is%20the%20social%20responsibility%20of%20the%20teacher.%20Those%20who%20say%20that%20teachers%20should%20only%20be%20concerned%20with%20their%20classroom%20and%20limit%20themselves%20to%20the%20task%20of%20completing%20the%20syllabus%2C%20do%20not%20know%20anything%20about%20the%20role%20of%20teachers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20happened%20to%20Kumar%20is%20happening%20quietly%20in%20other%20universities%2C%20especially%20the%20private%20universities%2C%20and%20we%20are%20often%20not%20aware%20of%20it.%20Private%20universities%20hire%20teachers%20in%20subjects%20such%20as%20journalism%20or%20mass%20communication%20on%20short-term%20contracts.%20It%20is%20their%20choice%20whether%20to%20continue%20the%20contract%20or%20not.%20But%20we%20have%20been%20hearing%20about%20the%20contracts%20of%20temporary%20teachers%2C%20who%20are%20considered%20inconvenient%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20not%20being%20renewed%20or%20terminated.%20It%20is%20difficult%20for%20all%20such%20teachers%20to%20go%20public%20with%20this%20information%20for%20obvious%20reasons.%20It%20might%20affect%20their%20chances%20of%20employment%20at%20a%20new%20place.%20No%20institution%20would%20like%20to%20hire%20a%20person%20disagreeable%20to%20the%20regime.%20So%20most%20of%20them%20keep%20quiet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20easy%20for%20the%20government%20to%20crack%20down%20on%20private%20universities.%20Their%20patrons%20are%20usually%20industrialists%20and%20businessmen.%20The%20government%20can%20attack%20their%20business%20on%20any%20pretext%20from%20questioning%20their%20land%20use%20to%20disconnecting%20water%20or%20electricity%20supply%20and%20withdrawing%20permission%20for%20new%20buildings%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECan%20any%20institution%20afford%20so%20much%20trouble%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20the%20freedom%20of%20public%20expression%20of%20one%20teacher%3F%20So%20even%20though%20patrons%20with%20good%20intentions%20tell%20teachers%20that%20they%20have%20complete%20freedom%20in%20their%20classes%2C%20they%20should%20keep%20their%20mouths%20shut%20outside.%20At%20least%20it%20will%20save%20the%20university.%20This%20is%20why%20you%20will%20hardly%20see%20articles%20on%20%E2%80%98sensitive%20topics%E2%80%99%20private%20university%20teachers%20in%20newspapers%20and%20other%20media%20platforms.%20It%20is%20not%20that%20they%20have%20changed%20their%20views%20or%20are%20scared.%20They%20have%20gone%20silent%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20their%20organisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20this%20is%20not%20happening%20at%20Delhi%20University%20right%20now%2C%20the%20government%20is%20trying%20to%20change%20the%20service%20conditions%20of%20teachers%20and%20put%20restrictions%20on%20their%20public%20writing%20or%20activity.%20Many%20central%20institutions%20have%20done%20this.%20This%20step%20gets%20support%20in%20the%20society%20because%20there%20is%20a%20general%20understanding%20that%20those%20who%20get%20salaries%20from%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20money%20do%20not%20have%20the%20right%20to%20criticise%20the%20government.%20But%20this%20understanding%20itself%20is%20flawed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPublic%20resources%20should%20be%20used%20in%20public%20interest.%20There%20is%20always%20a%20tension%20between%20public%20interest%20and%20power.%20Often%2C%20those%20in%20power%20force%20the%20public%20to%20consider%20their%20own%20interest%20as%20public%20interest.%20It%20is%20the%20job%20of%20those%20working%20in%20the%20field%20of%20knowledge%20production%20to%20keep%20the%20public%20aware%20of%20this%20tension%20and%20conflict.%20Their%20public%20speaking%20or%20writing%20is%20necessary%2C%20not%20for%20themselves%2C%20but%20for%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20public.%20How%20else%20will%20the%20facts%20given%20by%20the%20government%20and%20the%20reasons%20given%20for%20its%20decisions%20be%20tested%20or%20judged%3F%20This%20is%20where%20academics%20have%20a%20role%20to%20play.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20surprising%20that%20the%20relations%20between%20those%20in%20power%20and%20intellectuals%20are%20not%20generally%20cordial.%20But%20a%20totalitarian%20ideology%20considers%20them%20as%20its%20enemies.%20That%20is%20what%20we%E2%80%99re%20seeing%20in%20India%20right%20now.%20The%20government%20does%20not%20want%20to%20allow%20any%20other%20voice%20in%20the%20country%20except%20their%20own.%20Certainly%20not%20the%20calm%2C%20civilised%20and%20reasoned%20voice%20of%20a%20person%20like%20Kumar%20who%20chose%20freedom%20of%20his%20voice%20over%20his%20job.%20What%20did%20Lovely%20University%20choose%3F%20And%20do%20his%20students%20realise%20what%20has%20been%20taken%20away%20from%20them%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.thewire.in%2Fbyline%2Fapoorvanand%5C%22%3EApoorvanand%3C%2Fa%3E%20teaches%20at%20Delhi%20University.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711276046000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2F29112534%2Fcensorship.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fwhere-are-the-don-quixotes-of-indian-academia%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Those%20who%20say%20that%20teachers%20should%20only%20be%20concerned%20with%20their%20classroom%20and%20limit%20themselves%20to%20the%20task%20of%20completing%20the%20syllabus%2C%20do%20not%20know%20anything%20about%20the%20role%20of%20teachers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fwhere-are-the-don-quixotes-of-indian-academia%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Endrick%3A%20Who%20is%20Brazil's%20latest%20football%20prodigy%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711275900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F03%2F768x432%2Fskynews-endrick-brazil-england_6499582.jpg%3F20240324122422%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fendrick-who-is-brazils-latest-football-prodigy-13101012%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Under%20the%20famous%20Wembley%20arch%20on%20Saturday%20night%2C%20a%20new%20Brazilian%20prodigy%20announced%20himself%20to%20the%20world.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A70%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fendrick-who-is-brazils-latest-football-prodigy-13101012%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fendrick-who-is-brazils-latest-football-prodigy-13101012%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.co