ls%20of%20smuggled%20gold%20biscuits.%20The%20action%20sequences%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ELootere%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20have%20the%20focus%20and%20momentum%20that%20Mehta%20Sr%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EFaraaz%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20did.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20might%20be%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20leap%20for%20some%2C%20but%20I%E2%80%99d%20like%20to%20call%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ELootere%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20as%20the%20more%20well-rounded%20cousin%20of%20Hansal%20Mehta%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EScam%201992%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EScam%202003%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20This%20one%E2%80%99s%20slightly%20less%20in%20awe%20of%20its%20protagonist%2C%20even%20as%20he%20goes%20around%20trying%20to%20perform%20miracles%20out%20of%20thin%20air.%20The%20show%20also%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20shy%20away%20from%20showing%20him%20in%20a%20less-than-flattering%20light%2C%20especially%20in%20scenes%20where%20the%20son%20overhears%20his%20parents%20shouting%20abuses%20at%20each%20other%20during%20a%20particularly%20tense%20phone%20call.%20And%20therefore%2C%20the%20tragedy%20that%20befalls%20most%20of%20the%20characters%20feels%20earned%2C%20rather%20than%20simply%20being%20literary%20vindication.%20After%20all%2C%20desperation%20is%20the%20only%20language%20universally%20understood.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20first%20two%20episodes%20of%20Lootere%20are%20streaming%20on%20Disney%2BHotstar%2C%20the%20rest%20will%20be%20dropped%20once%20a%20week.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711271997000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F24144608%2FScreenshot-2024-03-24-at-2.44.03%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Flootere-hansal-mehta-somalia-disney-hotstar%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Often%