like%20this%2C%20a%20cup%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Echai%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20will%20not%20merely%20be%20sipped%20by%20someone%2C%20like%20it%20usually%20happens%20in%20films.%20The%20cup%20will%20slip%20from%20said%20person%E2%80%99s%20hand%2C%20spill%20onto%20the%20adjacent%20person%2C%20who%20will%20accidentally%20drop%20the%20leash%20of%20their%20pet%2C%20which%20will%20run%20away%20and%20get%20electrocuted%20by%20the%20nearby%20electric%20pole.%20Or%20such%20are%20the%20gags.%20You%20get%20the%20drift%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FB7VP47oCZfE%3Fsi%3Do92IXKOs563dSqnX%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20to%20say%20that%20such%20films%20are%20too%20%E2%80%98dated%E2%80%99%2C%20because%20the%20writing%20can%20hold%20a%20surprise%20every%20now%20and%20then.%20It%E2%80%99s%20something%20we%20saw%20glimpses%20of%20in%20Amar%20Kaushik%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EStree%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(2018)%20%E2%80%93%20a%20film%20that%20used%20the%20mould%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98boys%20comedy%E2%80%99%20to%20deliver%20commentary%20far%20more%20progressive%20than%20many%20of%20us%20would%20have%20expected%20from%20a%20film%20like%20that.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKunal%20Kemmu%20%E2%80%93%20who%20made%20a%20name%20for%20himself%20with%20his%20glorious%20comic-timing%20in%20films%20like%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EGo%20Goa%20Gone%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(2013)%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ELootcase%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(2020)%20%E2%80%93%20makes%20his%20directorial%20debut%20here.%20The%20film%20follows%20three%20childhood%20friends%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%20Dodo%20(Divyenndu)%2C%20Pinku%20(Pratik%20Gandhi)%20and%20Ayush%20(Avinash%20Tiwary)%20%E2%80%93%20desperate%20to%20make%20good%20on%20their%20plan%20for%20a%20Goa%20vacation.%20Excel%20Entertainment%20%E2%80%93%20the%20production%20house%20which%20seems%20to%20have%20patented%20the%20premise%20of%20three%20friends%20going%20on%20a%20trip%20%E2%80%94%20is%20the%20producer%20here.%20So%2C%20while%20the%20intent%20is%20to%20slight%20earlier%20films%20made%20by%20Excel%20like%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EDil%20Chahta%20Hai%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EZindagi%20Na%20Milegi%20Dobara%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20self-awareness%20feels%20too%20airbrushed%20and%20smug.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20laughed%20the%20loudest%20when%20the%20three%20friends%20reach%20a%20Goa%20shack%20and%20sipping%20a%20beer%20each%2C%20and%20Dodo%20asks%20the%20other%20two%3A%20%E2%80%9CEnjoy%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eho%20raha%20hai%20na%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%3F%20(we%E2%80%99re%20enjoying%2C%20right%3F)%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20A%20scene%20later%2C%20two%20of%20them%20are%20arguing%20with%20a%20jet-ski%20instructor%20about%20how%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20ride%20pillion%20because%20that%E2%80%99s%20not%20how%20it%20is%20shown%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EDil%20Chahta%20Hai%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20It%E2%80%99s%20also%20in%20this%20very%20scene%20that%20director%20Kemmu%20makes%20a%20special%20appearance%20as%20a%20dopey%20stranger%20sitting%20at%20a%20bar%2C%20distributing%20drugs%20to%20the%20three%20friends%20by%20calling%20them%20%E2%80%98background%20music%E2%80%99%20for%20their%20Goa%20trip.%20It%E2%80%99s%20where%20the%20film%20teases%20how%20funny%20it%20could%E2%80%99ve%20been%20as%20the%20realistic%2C%20antithesis%20version%20for%20all%20the%20road%20trips%20glorified%20in%20Bollywood.%20However%2C%20things%20get%20far%20more%20conventional%20after%20this.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20c