ms%20into%20something%20a%20Sandeep%20Reddy%20Vanga%20hero%20would%20look%20up%20to.%20I%20could%20somehow%20never%20quite%20buy%20the%20friendship%20between%20the%20three%20men%2C%20given%20how%20easy%20it%20is%20to%20pick%20apart%20Dodo%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98fake%20life%E2%80%99%20on%20Facebook.%20I%20kept%20waiting%20for%20the%20friends%20to%20come%20clean%20to%20Dodo%2C%20instead%20of%20the%20other%20way%20round.%20I%20was%20hoping%20they%20would%20tell%20him%20how%20they%20knew%20he%20was%20a%20penniless%2C%20unemployable%20man-child%2C%20but%20didn%E2%80%99t%20bring%20it%20up%20earlier%20to%20save%20him%20the%20embarrassment.%20Alas%2C%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20and%20Dodo%20gets%20an%20entire%20scene%20of%20a%20melodramatic%20confession%20%E2%80%93%20where%20a%20few%20tears%20resolve%20the%20whole%20thing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKemmu%20gives%20away%20his%20gaze%20during%20the%20scenes%20when%20Gandhi%20and%20Divyenndu%20crossdress%20into%20sarees%20to%20infiltrate%20a%20drug%20den.%20There%20are%20repeated%20references%20to%20the%20men%20to%20%E2%80%98adjust%20their%20oranges%E2%80%99%20with%20the%20background%20score%20harking%20back%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9890s%20Govinda%20movies.%20Kemmu%E2%80%99s%20collaborators%20%E2%80%93%20Raj%20%26amp%3B%20DK%20%E2%80%93%20would%20never%20go%20for%20such%20low%20hanging%20fruits%20(the%20pun%20is%20unfortunate).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHumour%20can%20often%20be%20subjective%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20impossible%20to%20write%20a%20genuinely%20funny%20line%20that%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20lose%20steam%20by%20the%20time%20it%20changes%20hands%20hundreds%20of%20times%2C%20by%20the%20time%20it%20reaches%20the%20audience%20in%20a%20theatre.%20Looking%20at%20all%20that%2C%20one%20could%20call%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMadgaon%20Express%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20a%20respectable%2C%20adequate%20debut.%20As%20the%20film%E2%80%99s%20final%20few%20minutes%20culminate%20into%20a%20Me