i%20run%20the%20Fomo%20Momo%20food%20truck%20in%20New%20Jersey%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Ankita%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20at%20the%20food%20festival%2C%20amidst%20the%20stalls%20that%20had%20Filipino%20food%2C%20Mexican%20food%2C%20Japanese%20food%20and%20more%2C%20there%20was%20a%20stall%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F306970%2Finspired-by-mom-entrepreneur-opens-nepali-restaurant-in-uttarakhand-mitho-thakali%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndian%20momos%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20Ankita%20and%20Impreet%20watched%20with%20bated%20breath%20as%20people%20came%20to%20see%20what%20the%20hype%20was%20all%20about.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20gave%20us%20a%20chance%20to%20test%20the%20market.%20What%20we%20observed%20was%20that%20though%20people%20did%20not%20know%20much%20about%20the%20momos%2C%20they%20wanted%20to%20try%20it%20out.%20Once%20they%20sampled%20it%2C%20they%20would%20return%20for%20some%20more.%20We%20developed%20a%20small%20fan%20base%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20share.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESensing%20that%20the%20idea%20would%20do%20well%2C%20the%20duo%20bought%20a%20food%20truck%20and%20started%20a%20business%20in%202023.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20they%20add%20that%20they%20continue%20to%20serve%20momos%20at%20the%20World%20Trade%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20food%20festival%20in%20New%20York%20that%20runs%20from%20April%20through%20October.%20To%20cater%20to%20every%20diaspora%2C%20the%20menu%20is%20divided%20into%20subtle%20options.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20butter%20garlic%20momos%20are%20a%20hit%20with%20the%20Americans%20while%20the%20spicier%20options%20suit%20the%20Indian%20palate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20emphasise%2C%20however%2C%20that%20perfecting%20the%20momo%20recipe%20has%20been%20a%20challenge.%20Eight%20months%20of%20experimenting%20finally%20led%20them%20to%20come%20up%20with%20a%20momo%20that%20ha