t%20of%20possessing%20the%20forest%20land.%20But%20when%20they%20did%20not%20cooperate%2C%20the%20officials%20asked%20them%20to%20vacate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20carrying%20eviction%20drives%20in%20this%20particular%20area%20was%20a%20big%20challenge%20for%20us.%20Our%20teams%20were%20attacked%20twice%20leading%20to%20injuries.%20My%20car%20was%20burnt%20down.%20It%20was%20heartbreaking%20for%20me%20to%20see%20my%20own%20people%20being%20beaten%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20manage%20this%20situation%2C%20I%20announced%20on%20a%20loudspeaker%20that%20since%20they%20injured%20forest%20officials%2C%20the%20police%20would%20book%20the%20masses%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20gathered%20mob%20had%20asked%20the%20women%20and%20the%20children%20of%20their%20community%20to%20stand%20before%20us.%20To%20avoid%20any%20hassles%20or%20misplaced%20blame%2C%20we%20had%20a%20force%20of%20female%20forest%20rangers%20on%20the%20sidelines%20too.%20There%20were%20even%20attempts%20to%20give%20this%20whole%20incident%20a%20communal%20angle%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20dwellers%20went%20on%20to%20file%20petitions%20at%20the%20National%20Commission%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribes%2C%20the%20State%20Commission%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribes%2C%20and%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20High%20Court%20against%20the%20Forest%20Department.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20the%20judgement%20was%20passed%20in%20our%20favour%20as%20we%20had%20all%20the%20evidence%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20order%20dated%2020%20June%2C%202023%2C%20the%20high%20court%20disposed%20of%20the%20writ%20petition%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cencroachers%E2%80%9D%20and%20mentioned%20that%20the%20respondents%20are%20%E2%80%9Cfree%20to%20take%20appropriate%20steps%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20rules%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20