ed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20has%20also%20helped%20us%20build%20trust%20among%20other%20local%20villagers%20who%20have%20now%20become%20our%20sources%20for%20sharing%20information%20on%20poaching-related%20incidences.%20Within%20nine%20months%2C%20we%20were%20able%20to%20conduct%2032%20operations%20where%20we%20arrested%20134%20poachers%20and%20smugglers.%20With%20reduced%20poaching%20and%20encroachment%20cases%2C%20we%20believe%20tigers%20from%20neighbouring%20states%20will%20find%20safe%20shelter%20and%20repopulate%20the%20reserve%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPersonally%2C%20this%20work%20has%20also%20brought%20immense%20contentment%20to%20Jain.%20%E2%80%9CBefore%20becoming%20an%20IFS%20officer%2C%20I%20wished%20to%20join%20the%20Delhi%20police%20force%20but%20I%20missed%20it%20by%20seven%20marks.%20This%20project%20made%20me%20do%20similar%20investigation%20work%20%E2%80%94%20from%20using%20the%20cyber%20cell%20to%20tracking%20call%20records%20and%20encroaching%20activities.%20I%20do%20not%20regret%20my%20decision%20anymore%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20India%2C%20an%20official%20uniform%20has%20been%20given%20to%20only%20three%20units%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Army%2C%20the%20police%2C%20and%20the%20forest%20officials.%20The%20purpose%20of%20this%20uniform%20is%20to%20provide%20protection.%20It%20is%20our%20duty%20to%20protect%20our%20natural%20heritage.%20Anyone%20can%20plant%20trees.%20But%20as%20a%20forest%20official%2C%20if%20we%20cannot%20save%20a%20tree%2C%20then%20what%20is%20the%20point%20of%20new%20afforestation%20drives%3F%E2%80%9D%20remarks%20Jain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%20All%20photos%3A%20IFS%20Varun%20Jain.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3C%2Fem%3E%3A%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fw