ce%20is%20free%20for%20customers.%20For%20people%20who%20need%20basic%20information%2C%20they%20also%20provide%20information%20and%20FAQs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20initial%20idea%20behind%20starting%20this%20platform%20was%20to%20educate%20people.%20Exposure%20to%20knowledge%20and%20access%20to%20basic%20legalities%20is%20sorely%20missing%20here.%20We%20provide%20you%20with%20all%20the%20information%20that%20you%20need%20even%20before%20visiting%20a%20lawyer.%20You%20want%20to%20file%20an%20FIR%3F%20Here%E2%80%99s%20a%20template%20which%20you%20just%20need%20to%20fill%20in%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20the%20young%20lawyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20different%20packages%20that%20Rest%20the%20Case%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F295748%2Fkochi-law-student-breaks-stereotypes-about-women-bus-drivers-ann-mary%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprovides%20to%20lawyers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20allow%20them%20to%20help%20with%20leads%20and%20display%20their%20profile.%20They%20also%20provide%20a%20Client%20Management%20System%20(CMS)%20to%20help%20the%20lawyers%20manage%20and%20document%20the%20data.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESiddhant%20Deshpande%2C%20a%20criminal%20lawyer%20practising%20at%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court%2C%20states%20that%20Rest%20The%20Case%20has%20helped%20him%20with%20over%2010%20leads%20so%20far%2C%20which%20is%20helpful%20for%20young%20lawyers%20to%20gain%20a%20good%20customer%20base%20and%20handle%20a%20variety%20of%20cases.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20found%20the%20company%20through%20social%20media.%20What%20is%20unique%20about%20them%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20give%20you%20verified%20leads%20(clients)%20and%20help%20you%20with%20all%20the%20background%20information.%20They%20give%20you%20a%20pretty%20good%20deal%20and%20think%20about%20the%20welfare%20of%20both%20the%20clients%20and%20the%20lawyers%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Siddhant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%2C%20how%20are%20the%20lawyers%20vetted%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEach%20lawyer%E2%80%99s%20information%20is%20cross%20checked%20with%20the%20bar%20council.%20We%20verify%20their%20credentials%20through%20their%20bar%20council%20number%2C%E2%80%9D%20states%20Shreya.%20The%20lawyers%20using%20the%20website%20have%20an%20experience%20of%20anywhere%20between%20three%20and%20twenty%20years%2C%20bringing%20in%20a%20traffic%20of%20about%20200-300%20customers%20every%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20their%20study%2C%20most%20of%20the%20clients%20on%20Rest%20The%20Case%20are%20using%20assistance%20for%20either%20divorce%20or%20family%20law%20cases%2C%20or%20property%20disputes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20team%20of%2015%2C%20the%20CEO%20is%20looking%20to%20bring%20in%20lawyers%20from%20more%20cities%20across%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20most%20people%20get%20frazzled%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20matters%20of%20the%20court%2C%20the%20ease%20and%20one-on-one%20help%20that%20the%20platform%20provides%20has%20become%20their%20USP.%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99ve%20made%20access%20to%20legal%20information%20as%20simple%20as%20clicking%20a%20button%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20lawyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20appropriate%20exposure%20matters%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Frest-the-case-2-1710763616.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shreya%20Sharma%20wants%20to%20simplify%20legal%20jargon%20and%20make%20legal%20aid%20accessible%20to%20all%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Frest-the-case-2-1710763616.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Frest-the-case-2-1710763616-225x30