t%20The%20Case%E2%80%99%20that%20discusses%20latest%20legal%20developments%20and%20decodes%20the%20intricacies%20of%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20is%20there%20any%20legal%20advice%20that%20she%20would%20give%20to%20everyone%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20should%20be%20aware%20of%20the%20laws%20that%20concern%20you.%20Legal%20knowledge%20is%20just%20as%20important%20as%20financial%20education.%20As%20consumers%2C%20being%20aware%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F344779%2Fworld-consumers-rights-day-landmark-judgements-consumer-law-in-india-online-orders%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econsumer%20rights%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20of%20paramount%20importance.%20Read%20up%20on%20things%20related%20to%20you%20and%20your%20line%20of%20work.%20Know%20your%20rights%20as%20a%20tenant%20or%20property%20owner%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%2C%20Pictures%20Courtesy%20Shreya%20Sharma)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710766089000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Frest-the-case-3-min-1710763667.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D345065%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shreya%20Sharma%20started%20'Rest%20The%20Case'%20in%202021%2C%20a%20legal%20aggregator%20platform%20that%20provides%20a%20list%20of%201%2C200%20specialised%20lawyers%20across%20200%20cities%20in%20India.%20It%20also%20provides%20basic%20legal%20templates%20like%20rent%20agreements%20and%20explains%20legal%20terms%20that%20everyone%20should%20know.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F345065%2Fhow-to-find-a-lawyer-legal-startup-pune-shreya-sharma-divorce-family-court-business-property-law-rent-agreement%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20to%20Grow%20Raspberries%2C%20Blueberries%20in%20India%3F%20Woman%20Uses%20Low-Cost%20Innovation%20to%20Run%20Berry%20Biz%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEvery%20year%2C%20tonnes%20of%20exotic%20fruits%20including%20blueberries%20and%20raspberries%20are%20imported%20for%20urban%20Indian%20consumers%20owing%20to%20their%20wide%20range%20of%20health%20benefits.%20Data%20shows%20that%20raspberry%2C%20blackberry%2C%20blueberry%2C%20and%20cranberry%20imports%20into%20India%20skyrocketed%20to%20870%20tonnes%20in%202022%20%E2%80%93%20indicating%20a%20surge%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indexbox.io%2Fsearch%2Fprice-for-raspberry-blackberry-blueberry-and-cranberry-india%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIn%25202022%252C%2520raspberry%252C%2520blackberry%252C%2C616%2525%2520against%2520the%2520previous%2520year.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E148%20percent%3C%2Fa%3E%20compared%20to%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20US%20Highbush%20Blueberry%20Council%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Fmarkets%2Fcommodities%2Fdemand-for-us-blueberry-rising-in-india%2Farticle34852525.ece%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUSHBC%3C%2Fa%3E)%2C%20the%20imports%20of%20blueberries%20in%20fresh%20and%20dried%20forms%20grew%20from%20almost%20zero%20in%202009%20to%201%2C900%20tonnes%20in%202020%2C%20making%20India%20one%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20top%20importers%20of%20blueberries.%20This%20trade%20between%20the%20United%20States%20and%20India%20is%20growing%20at%20a%20rate%20of%20around%2030%20percent%20per%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20these%20numbers%20are%20rising%20annually%2C%20Maharashtra%E2%80%99s%20Keya%20Salot%20has%20stepped%20up%20to%20bring%20these%20numbers%20down%20to%20some%20extent.%20%E2%80%9CIn%202021-22%2C%20India%20was%20importing%20%242.2%20billion%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F313743%2Fchethan-shetty-quit-corporate-job-to-become-farmer-in-bellare-mangaluru-earns-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexotic%20fruits%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20vegetables.%20That%E2%80%99s%20not%20really%20a%20good%20number.%20I%20wanted%20to%20get%20into%20the%20sector%20to%20cultivate%20these%20exotic%20varieties%20locally.%20By%20doing%20this%2C%20it%20would%20also%20make%20them%20affordable%20for%20consumers%20beyond%20metros%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Keya%20set%20up%20Farm2Fam%20to%20cultivate%20these%20exotic%20berries.%20Today%2C%20she%20has%20scaled%20up%20the%20production%20on%2020%20acres%20of%20land%20and%20estimates%20a%20production%20of%20at%20least%20135%20tonnes%20of%20berries%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fkeya-salot-4-1710700215.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Blueberries%20and%20raspberries%20are%20cultivated%20largely%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20Russia%2C%20Mexico%2C%20Serbia%2C%20and%20Poland.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fkeya-salot-4-1710700215.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fkeya-salot-4-1710700215-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fkeya-salot-4-1710700215-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fkeya-salot-4-1710700215-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fkeya-salot-4-1710700215-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345042%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBlueberries%20and%20raspberries%20are%20cultivated%20largely%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20Russia%2C%20Mexico%2C%20Serbia%2C%20and%20Poland.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20she%20sheds%20light%20on%20the%20innovative%20methods%20that%20helped%20her%20cultivate%20berries%20in%20the%20harsh%20weather%20conditions%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EQuit%20law%20to%20become%20a%20farmer%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20brought%20up%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20Keya%20was%20a%20lawyer%20by%20profession.%20After%20pursuing%20law%20from%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20Government%20Law%20College%2C%20she%20continued%20her%20practice%20with%20law%20firms%20for%20nearly%20four%20years%20until%20she%20understood%20her%20calling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20always%20wanted%20to%20become%20a%20farmer.%20For%20me%2C%20the%20idea%20of%20pursuing%20law%20was%20always%20to%20later%20focus%20on%20entrepreneurship.%20But%20before%20that%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20get%20good%20access%20to%20the%20legal%20framework%20to%20build%20a%20successful%20business.%20I%20wanted%20to%20work%20in%20an%20impactful%20sector%20to%20create%20a%20very%20purpose-driven%20entrepreneurship%20programme%20which%20would%20not%20only%20benefit%20me%20personally%20but%20would%20also%20benefit%20the%20society%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%2032-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20she%20took%20a%20break%20from%20work%20to%20understand%20the%20nitty-gritties%20of%20farming%20as%20she%20did%20not%20have%20any%20agricultural%20background.%20To%20begin%20with%2C%20Keya%20started%20growing%20about%2030%20varieties%20of%20microgreens%20in%20a%20vertical%20set-up%20made%20on%20the%20terrace.%20Soon%2C%20she%20started%20supplying%20them%20to%20restaurants%2C%20and%20within%20six%20months%2C%20she%20on-boarded%2050%20clients.%20This%20boosted%20her%20confidence%20and%20allowed%20her%20to%20establish%20retail%20connections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20this%20transition%2C%20I%20started%20researching%20on%20the%20kinds%20of%20crops%20grown%20in%20other%20countries%20that%20had%20gained%20a%20lot%20of%20traction%20in%20agriculture.%20Compared%20to%20countries%20in%20South%20and%20Central%20America%2C%20India%20has%20not%20graduated%20beyond%20growing%20major%20basic%20crops%20like%20paddy%2C%20sugarcane%2C%20and%20wheat%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fkeya-salot-1-1-1710699243.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%202021%2C%20Keya%20set%20up%20Farm2Fam%20to%20cultivate%20exotic%20berries.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fkeya-salot-1-1-1710699243.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fkeya-salot-1-1-1710699243-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fkeya-salot-1-1-1710699243-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fkeya-salot-1-1-1710699243-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fkeya-salot-1-1-1710699243-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345039%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIn%202021%2C%20Keya%20set%20up%20Farm2Fam%20to%20cultivate%20exotic%20berries.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20today%2C%20despite%20a%20significant%20portion%20of%20the%20economy%20and%20the%20population%20being%20dependent%20on%20agriculture%2C%20we%20are%20not%20able%20to%20produce%20high-value%20crops.%20We%20needed%20to%20choose%20crops%20that%20will%20get%20a%20slightly%20longer%20cycle%20but%20will%20give%20definitive%20returns%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20year%20of%20research%2C%20Keya%20zeroed%20down%20to%20cultivating%20the%20crop%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F34505%2Fraspberry-pi-kits-for-school-children-in-kerala%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblueberries%20and%20raspberries%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%93%20cultivated%20largely%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20Russia%2C%20Mexico%2C%20Serbia%2C%20and%20Poland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMaking%20foreign%20crops%20adaptable%20with%20innovative%20methods%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKeya%20shares%20the%20major%20challenge%20in%20cultivating%20these%20exotic%20varieties%20was%20to%20make%20them%20adaptable%20to%20the%20Indian%20weather%20conditions.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20blueberries%20require%20cold%20winters%20and%20moderate%20to%20high%20rainfall%20throughout%20its%20growing%20season%2C%20raspberries%20are%20also%20suited%20to%20temperate%20regions%20with%20cool%20summers%20and%20mild%20winters%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20late%202019%2C%20Keya%20along%20with%20her%20husband%2C%20Vimal%20Salot%2C%20visited%20Mexico%20and%20Europe%20which%20had%20similar%20geometric%20conditions%20to%20Maharashtra.%20In%202020%2C%20she%20imported%20the%20first%20set%20of%20saplings%20adaptable%20to%20Indian%20weather%20conditions%20and%20harvested%20the%20first%20commercial%20yield%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fkeya-salot-2-1710699316.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Keya%20installed%20low-cost%20tunnels%20in%20about%2080%20percent%20of%20her%20farm.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fkeya-salot-2-1710699316.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fkeya-salot-2-1710699316-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fkeya-salot-2-1710699316-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fkeya-salot-2-1710699316-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fkeya-salot-2-1710699316-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345040%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKeya%20installed%20low-cost%20tunnels%20in%20about%2080%20percent%20of%20her%20farm.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20cultivate%20them%20in%20the%20tropical%20climate%20of%20Maharashtra%2C%20Keya%20opted%20for%20the%20tunnel%20method%20of%20cultivation%20that%20overcame%20the%20drawbacks%20of%20extreme%20weather%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20required%20to%20protect%20crops%20like%20raspberries%20and%20blueberries%20from%20extreme%20temperatures.%20Currently%2C%20India%20only%20has%20poly%20houses%20as%20an%20infrastructure%20for%20protected%20cultivation%2C%20and%20in%20geographical%20climates%20like%20Maharashtra%2C%20we%20need%20protection%20from%20harsh%20conditions%20rather%20than%20adding%20heat%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20we%20developed%20our%20own%20low-cost%20tunnel%20structures%20for%20growing%20these%20berries%20where%20we%20can%20add%20or%20remove%20the%20plastic%20cover%20as%20per%20the%20weather%20requirements%20and%20maintain%20ideal%20temperature%20conditions%20for%20the%20growth%20of%20plants.%20With%20this%2C%20we%20can%20now%20provide%20a%20warmer%20climate%20during%20the%20winter%20nights%20and%20cooler%20conditions%20for%20growth%20during%20the%20summer%20days%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20protecting%20the%20crops%20from%20rain.%20This%20technique%20has%20its%20origin%20in%20the%20European%20countries%20where%20they%20use%20the%20structure%20to%20protect%20the%20heat%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKeya%20installed%20low-cost%20tunnels%20in%20about%2080%20percent%20of%20her%20farm%20and%20is%20cultivating%20at%20least%20seven%20varieties%20of%20exotic%20berries.%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F343071%2Fhow-to-grow-strawberries-dragon-fruit-turmeric-terrace-gardening%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGrowing%20blueberries%3C%2Fa%3E%20under%20high%20tunnels%20protects%20them%20from%20extremes%20of%20temperature%2C%20requires%20less%20water%2C%20and%20yields%20more%20fruit.%20This%20method%20also%20helps%20blueberries%20ripen%20earlier.%20Instead%20of%20the%20usual%20harvest%20period%20that%20lasts%20only%20for%20a%20few%20weeks%2C%20we%20can%20harvest%20yields%20for%20four%20to%20five%20months%20with%20this%20method%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fkeya-salot-3-1710700136.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Keya%20expects%20a%20bountiful%20harvest%20of%20at%20least%20135%20tonnes%20of%20berries%20this%20season.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fkeya-salot-3-1710700136.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fkeya-salot-3-1710700136-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fkeya-salot-3-1710700136-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fkeya-salot-3-1710700136-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fkeya-salot-3-1710700136-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345041%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKeya%20expects%20a%20bountiful%20harvest%20of%20at%20least%20135%20tonnes%20of%20berries%20this%20season.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20one%20of%20the%20other%20challenges%20she%20faced%20in%20setting%20up%20the%20farm%20business%20in%20Talegaon%2C%20Pune%2C%20Keya%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CGetting%20access%20to%20land%20was%20extremely%20difficult%20for%20us%20as%20it%20was%20very%20difficult%20to%20convince%20a%20farmer%20to%20lease%20their%20land%20to%20a%20city%20dweller.%20As%20you%20do%20not%20have%20a%20base%20in%20a%20village%2C%20it%20invites%20a%20lot%20of%20aversion.%20But%20after%203%20to%204%20months%20of%20trying%20our%20hands%2C%20we%20got%20our%20first%20piece%20of%20land.%20It%20took%20some%20time%20to%20build%20trust%20among%20the%20farmers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20she%20has%20expanded%20the%20production%20on%2020%20acres%20of%20land%20and%20expects%20a%20bountiful%20harvest%20of%20at%20least%20135%20tonnes%20of%20berries%20this%20season.%20As%20of%20now%2C%20she%20has%20collaborated%20with%20delivery%20partners%20like%20Swiggy%20and%20Zepto%2C%20and%20supermarkets%20like%20Star%20Bazaar%2C%20KisanKonnect%2C%20Reliance%20Retail%2C%20and%20Nature%E2%80%99s%20Basket%20to%20deliver%20the%20produce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20her%20transition%20from%20being%20a%20lawyer%20to%20an%20innovative%20farmer%2C%20Keya%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20perception%20that%20agriculture%20is%20not%20a%20profitable%20business.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20a%20huge%20portion%20of%20our%20economy%20rests%20on%20it.%20It%20is%20the%20responsibility%20of%20people%20with%20exposure%20to%20change%20this%20perception%20rather%20than%20fear%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20feel%20if%20I%20had%20only%20practiced%20law%