%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_0999_11zon-1710330407.jpg%202407w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_0999_11zon-1710330407-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_0999_11zon-1710330407-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_0999_11zon-1710330407-768x432.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_0999_11zon-1710330407-1536x863.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_0999_11zon-1710330407-2048x1151.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_0999_11zon-1710330407-150x84.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-344742%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221353%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESumanti%E2%80%99s%20stall%20at%20Samvaad%20sold%20Oraon%20paintings.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Mud%20and%20fingers%20are%20our%20USP%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20no%20records%20of%20when%20Oraon%20paintings%20originated.%20Sumanti%20says%20the%20paintings%20are%20several%20centuries%20old%20and%20were%20passed%20down%20from%20one%20generation%20to%20another.%20She%20grew%20up%20seeing%20her%20family%2C%20relatives%2C%20and%20neighbours%20do%20Oraon%20painting%20on%20the%20walls%20on%20various%20occasions%20in%20the%20Jashpur%20district%20of%20Chhattisgarh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCalendars%20did%20not%20exist%20for%20me.%20I%20could%20tell%20which%20month%20or%20festival%20was%20coming%20up%20based%20on%20the%20painting%20my%20mother%20did%20on%20our%20house%20walls.%20For%20instance%2C%20people%20would%20draw%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekaram%20%3C%2Fem%3Etree%20%3Cem%3E(Nauclea%20Parvifolia)%3C%2Fem%3E%20ahead%20of%20the%20harvest%20festival.%20Drawing%20an%20egg%20in%20between%20rice%20grains%20meant%20%3Cem%3EDanda%20Kattna%3C%2Fem%3E%20pooja%20for%20auspicious%20activities%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20peculiar%20thing%20about%20Oraon%20paintings%20is%20that%20mud%20forms%20the%20main%20base%20due%20to%20the%20availability%20of%20various%20types%20of%20soils.%20The%20community%20creates%20different%20shades%20of%20black%2C%20brown%20and%20red%20from%20the%20soil.%20Green%20and%20white%20colours%20are%20made%20from%20leaves%20and%20rice%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESumanti%20says%20she%20adds%20glue%20to%20the%20colours%20so%20that%20it%20sticks%20to%20the%20canvas.%20To%20date%2C%20she%20and%20the%20people%20from%20her%20village%20have%20not%20used%20acrylic%20or%20synthetic%20colours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20mentions%20two%20reasons%20for%20this%2C%20%E2%80%9CFirstly%2C%20accessibility%20and%20cost%20came%20in%20the%20way%2C%20and%20secondly%2C%20natural%20colours%20are%20a%20very%20important%20part%20of%20our%20identity.%20Our%20ancestors%20were%20confined%20to%20villages%2C%20so%20they%20made%20natural%20colours%20on%20their%20own%20and%20took%20pride%20in%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EColours%20that%20come%20from%20the%20soil%20are%20seen%20as%20sacred%2C%20she%20informs.%20The%20elders%20of%20the%20house%20perform%20a%20brief%20ritual%2C%20praying%20for%20an%20obstacle-free%20search%20for%20the%20right%20soil.%20While%20red%20and%20brown%20soils%20were%20readily%20accessible%2C%20finding%20black%20ones%20was%20challenging%20at%20that%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20ancestors%20would%20have%20to%20dig%20in%20forests%20to%20find%20the%20black%20soil.%20The%20rarity%20factor%20makes%20the%20soil%20so%20important%20in%20our%20culture.%20Besides%2C%20these%20three%20colours%20are%20used%20in%20all%20our%20%3Cem%3Epujas%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20date.%20According%20to%20a%20legend%2C%20Mahadev%20and%20Parvati%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20told%20our%20ancestors%20to%20use%20these%20colours%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20colours%2C%20the%20primary%20themes%20also%20remain%20intact%20in%20the%20Oraon%20paintings.%20Mostly%2C%20the%20paintings%20depict%20community%20life%20%E2%80%94%20including%20their%20dance%2C%20customs%2C%20forest%20deities%20and%20festivals.%20The%20making%20can%20take%20up%20to%2010%20to%2015%20days%20due%20to%20the%20layered%20process.%20Each%20layer%20has%20to%20dry%20before%20the%20second%20layer%20is%20completed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20all%20the%20paintings%2C%20Sumanti%20uses%20her%20fingers%20and%20cloth%20(for%20dabbing)%20even%20though%20the%20use%20of%20a%20brush%20is%20slowly%20penetrating%20the%20community%2C%20%E2%80%9CBut%20mud%20and%20fingers%20are%20our%20USP%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20these%20factors%20are%20what%20makes%20art%20so%20much%20more%20valuable%20and%20personal.%20The%20paintings%20do%20not%20preach%20or%20tell%20how%20one%20should%20live.%20Instead%2C%20it%20depicts%20Oraon%E2%80%99s%20culture%20most%20honestly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CArt%20is%20a%20lifelong%20teacher.%20It%20has%20taught%20me%20to%20be%20fair%20towards%20myself%20and%20make%20the%20best%20of%20my%20circumstances.%20It%20is%20a%20reminder%20that%20despite%20the%20harshness%20of%20life%2C%20financial%20burdens%2C%20incomplete%20dreams%20and%20frustrated%20days%2C%20it%20is%20okay.%20Every%20time%20I%20paint%2C%20it%20shows%20me%20the%20genuine%20merit%20of%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20960px)%20100vw%2C%20960px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FPhoto-credit-Sumanti-Devi-1710330421.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sumanti%20demonstrating%20her%20art%20to%20the%20participants%20of%20Samvaad.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FPhoto-credit-Sumanti-Devi-1710330421.jpeg%20960w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FPhoto-credit-Sumanti-Devi-1710330421-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FPhoto-credit-Sumanti-Devi-1710330421-500x333.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FPhoto-credit-Sumanti-Devi-1710330421-768x512.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FPhoto-credit-Sumanti-Devi-1710330421-150x100.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FPhoto-credit-Sumanti-Devi-1710330421-272x182.jpeg%20272w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-344746%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESumanti%20demonstrating%20her%20art%20to%20the%20participants%20of%20Samvaad.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESaving%20the%20fading%20art%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESumanti%20noticed%20migration%20and%20a%20decline%20in%20her%20village%E2%80%99s%20art%20over%20time.%20Her%20effort%20to%20take%20Oraon%20paintings%20to%20the%20popularity%20of%20Madhubani%20or%20Gond%20started%2015%20years%20ago.%20She%20pioneered%20the%20transition%20of%20these%20paintings%20from%20walls%20to%20cloth%20and%20handmade%20paper.%20Today%2C%20her%20artworks%20have%20journeyed%20across%20India%2C%20from%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20to%20Kerala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20started%20with%20a%20tribal%20art%20fair%20workshop%20in%20Bhubaneswar%20organised%20by%20Indira%20Gandhi%20Rashtriya%20Manav%20Sangrahalaya.%20We%20only%20sold%20one%20painting%2C%20but%20it%20gave%20us%20hope%20that%20if%20done%20correctly%2C%20it%20could%20be%20a%20viable%20option.%20A%20few%20years%20into%20doing%20exhibitions%20and%20local%20%3Cem%3Ehaats%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20I%20learnt%20about%20Samvaad.%20I%20joined%20the%20initiative%20as%20a%20fellow.%20As%20part%20of%20the%20fellowship%2C%20I%20released%20an%20art%20curation%20book%20titled%20%E2%80%98Evam%20Kala%E2%80%99%20on%20Oraon%20folklore%2C%20documenting%20the%20culture%20and%20traditions%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sumanti%2C%20who%20has%20a%20master%E2%80%99s%20degree%20in%20political%20science.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20shares%20that%20she%20also%20attends%20handicraft%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F344526%2Fsamvaad-tata-steel-foundation-celebrates-culture-of-tribes-of-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eart%20workshops%20by%20Samvaa%3C%2Fa%3Ed%20to%20learn%20about%20new%20market%20trends%20and%20skills%20that%20can%20help%20her%20with%20more%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20set%20up%20a%20stall%20in%20an%20exhibition%2C%20there%20is%20so%20much%20more%20than%20just%20selling%20the%20paintings.%20I%20learnt%20that%20if%20you%20wear%20traditional%20clothing%20in%20exhibitions%2C%20more%20people%20tend%20to%20visit%20your%20stall.%20The%20way%20you%20place%20your%20paintings%20in%20a%20small%20area%20also%20matters%20a%20lot.%20For%20example%2C%20always%20have%20a%20subtle%20and%20muted%20painting%20between%20two%20colourful%20paintings.%20It%20serves%20as%20a%20palette%20cleanser.%20Even%20the%20way%20you%20talk%20to%20people%20and%20tell%20your%20story%20matters.%20I%20learnt%20all%20this%20and%20more%20from%20experts%20who%20conduct%20Samvaad%20workshops%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sumanti%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FUntitled-design-1-1710338733.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sumanti%20Devi%20(L)%20Oraon%20painting%20in%20process.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FUntitled-design-1-1710338733.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2